NK041(di)037:1: // gangs ri'i khrod kyi klog pa nyan bshad pa rnams
NK041(di)037:2: kyi snyan du bsrings pa thos bsam 'chi med bdud
NK041(di)037:3: rtsi zhes bya ba bzhug so //
NK041(di)037:4: stobs bcu'i dbang phyug sh+aakya seng ge la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)037:5: gang gis byang chub spyod pa'i dus nas spang blang khrims kyis rgyud bsdams te /
NK041(di)037:6: mkhyen gsum la brten sbyor bzhi'i lam gyis chos sku'i go 'phang mngon gyur nas //
NK041(di)037:7: gzhan phyir bden gnyis zung 'jug las brtsams skyob pa nyid gzigs lam gsungs pas //
NK041(di)037:8: bral smin sku dang ye shes mchog sbyin sh+aakya'i gtso bos dge legs mdzod //
NK041(di)037:9: sde snod rgyud sde yan lag dang bcas pa'i //
NK041(di)037:10: lung gi dam chos nyan dang 'chad 'dod rnams //
NK041(di)037:11: bshes gnyen dam pa spyi bo'i thod bzhin bsten //
NK041(di)037:12: rgyal ba'i bka' dang tshad ldan mkhas pa'i gzhung //
NK041(di)037:13: rnam dpyod brtson pas thos dang bsam par bya //
NK041(di)037:14: log pa'i srol la nyin mtshan khor yug tu //
NK041(di)037:15: nan gyis bslab kyang ngal ba don med pas //
NK041(di)037:16: de phyir mkhas pa'i bshad srol 'di yin ces //
NK041(di)037:17: phyogs kyi bshes gnyen rnams la 'di bsrings so //
NK041(di)037:18: gangs can 'gro mang gtsug gi khrir 'khod pa //
NK041(di)037:19: spyan ras gzigs dbang sa skyong sprul pa'i sku //
NK041(di)037:20: sngon gyi chos rgyal lha gcig btsan po de //
NK041(di)037:22: gangs ri'i khrod kyi ston pa dang po yin //
NK041(di)037:23: gangs can smra ba'i srol 'byed sam+b+ho ta //
NK041(di)037:24: dgra bgegs log 'dren tshar gcod badz+ra sh+r+ai //
NK041(di)037:25: mdo sngags bstan pa'i gzhir gyur pa gor zhabs //
NK041(di)037:26: mtshungs bral bod kyi sgra bsgyur ska cog zhang //
NK041(di)037:27: snga 'gyur lo pan skyes mchog gi skor phal mo cher zur du gsal /
NK041(di)037:28: rgyal bas lung bstan sprul pa'i lo chen gnyis //
NK041(di)037:31: gnas lnga rig pa'i mthar son sa skya pa //
NK041(di)037:32: yongs rdzogs bstan pa'i mnga' bdag rin chen grub //
NK041(di)037:33: byang phyogs bshad rgyun 'degs pa'i ka chen bcu //
NK041(di)037:34: drang srong chen po thams cad gzigs pa yis //
NK041(di)037:35: 'gro kun byang chen dkri ba'i thems skas su //
NK041(di)037:36: 'khor lo rnam gsum 'dul mdo mngon rgyud sde bzhi bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med la sogs //
NK041(di)037:37: mdo sngags chos kyi dril chen 'dzam gling bsgrags //
NK041(di)037:38: legs gsungs 'dul ba'i pho brang nang zhugs nas //
NK041(di)037:39: nyis brgya lnga bcu pham pa bzhi /
NK041(di)037:44: nyes byas brgya dang bcu gnyis rnams so //
NK041(di)037:47: rab byung gso sbyong gzhi dang ni //
NK041(di)037:48: dgag dbye dbyar dang ko spags bzhi //
NK041(di)037:49: sman dang gos dang sra brkyang dang //
NK041(di)037:50: koo sham+b+hi dang las kyi gzhi //
NK041(di)037:51: dmar ser can dang gang zag dang //
NK041(di)037:52: spo dang gso sbyong bzhag pa dang //
NK041(di)037:53: gnas mal dang ni rtsod pa dang //
NK041(di)037:54: dge 'dun dbyen rnams bsdus pa yin //
NK041(di)037:56: bdun blang bya 'jug pa'i tshul khrims te //
NK041(di)037:57: 'khor lo dang po'i lam gyi rim pa'o //
NK041(di)037:58: 'phags pa'i yul du bsdu ba gnyis pa'i rjes //
NK041(di)037:59: mdo lung dgongs 'grel gyes pa bco brgyad byung //
NK041(di)037:60: sde pa tha dad rim par bsdus pa las /
NK041(di)037:61: shar nub ri dang gangs rir gnas //
NK041(di)037:63: rtag par smra ba'i sde snod ni //
NK041(di)037:64: lnga tshan dge 'dun phal chen pa //
NK041(di)037:65: bzhi pa dang ni 'od srungs sde //
NK041(di)037:66: sa ston sde dang chos srung ste //
NK041(di)037:67: mang thos gos dmar slob pa dang //
NK041(di)037:68: rnam par phye ste smra ba ni //
NK041(di)037:69: thams cad yod par smra ba'i sde //
NK041(di)037:70: rgyal byed tshal gnas 'jigs med ri //
NK041(di)037:71: gtsug lag khang chen gnas brtan pa'o //
NK041(di)037:72: sa sgrogs rigs dang srung ba pa //
NK041(di)037:73: gnas ma bu yi sde rnams ni //
NK041(di)037:74: kun gyis bkur ba rnam pa gsum //
NK041(di)037:75: yul don slob dpon bye brag gis //
NK041(di)037:76: tha dad rnam pa bco brgyad gyur //
NK041(di)037:78: de las sa ston sde pa'am dpe ston sde pa dang /
NK041(di)037:79: 'jig rten 'das par smra ba gnyis ni mdo sde pa dang /
NK041(di)037:80: lhag ma bcu drug po byed smra ba'i grub mtha' 'dzin pa kho na'o //
NK041(di)037:81: yod smra'i dgongs 'grel yon sh+aaka rnam gnyis dang //
NK041(di)037:82: bshes gnyen drug sogs 'phags yul mkhas rnams so //
NK041(di)037:83: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir bshad srol rnam gsum smad 'dul /
NK041(di)037:87: kun gyi bka' babs bu ston rin dri med bshes gnyen khyad par bshes gnyen /
NK041(di)037:91: chos kyi bshes gnyen rnams so //
NK041(di)037:97: khyung lhas pa sogs bu chen byung /
NK041(di)037:98: kha ba can 'dir 'phags mchog gnyis par gyur //
NK041(di)037:99: thar 'dod rnams kyang srol de'i rjes su zhugs //
NK041(di)037:100: mkhyen gsum thos bsam mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK041(di)037:101: shes rab pha rol phyin pa ni /
NK041(di)037:102: dngos po brgyad kyis yang dag bshad //
NK041(di)037:104: de nas thams cad shes 3pa nyid //
NK041(di)037:105: rnam kun 1mngon rdzogs rtogs pa dang //
NK041(di)037:107: skad cig 4gcig mngon rdzogs byang chub //
NK041(di)037:108: chos kyi sku 1dang de rnams brgyad //
NK041(di)037:109: ces skabs brgyad mngon rtogs don gnyis kyis 'chad do //
NK041(di)037:111: nyams len sbyor bzhi'i gzings la brten nas ni //
NK041(di)037:112: chos sku lhun po'i mdzes pa blta ba yi //
NK041(di)037:113: 'khor lo bar pa'i sbas don lam rim de //
NK041(di)037:114: dga' ldan gnas su mi pham chos rjes bkral //
NK041(di)037:115: 'phags pa'i yul du bka' babs rnam pa drug /
NK041(di)037:116: bde ba'i 'byung gnas dga' ldan lha yul /
NK041(di)037:117: longs spyod kyi 'byung gnas 'og klu yul /
NK041(di)037:118: rig pa'i 'byung gnas shar phyogs b+hang+ga la /
NK041(di)037:119: yon tan gyi 'byung gnas lho phyogs bee t+aa'i yul /
NK041(di)037:120: byin rlabs kyi 'byung gnas nub phyogs o rgyan yul /
NK041(di)037:121: ngo mtshar gyi 'byung gnas byang phyogs bi shwa ka tsan+dana gyi gling nas brgyud pa ste drug go //
NK041(di)037:122: rgyan gyi dgongs 'grel thogs med sku mched sogs /
NK041(di)037:124: gang de 'grel la 'phags 'phags pa grol sde dang /
NK041(di)037:125: slob dpon seng ge bzang po /
NK041(di)037:127: de dag bzhed gzhung rngog lo'i thugs mtshor babs //
NK041(di)037:128: sher phyin rgyas mdzad 'bre ar rnam gnyis kyi //
NK041(di)037:129: rngog lo'i slob ma 'bre shes rab 'bar dang /
NK041(di)037:130: de'i slob ma ar byang chub ye shes /
NK041(di)037:131: 'chad rtsom nyi zla'i 'od zer 'bum phrag gis //
NK041(di)037:132: gangs can mun pa'i nags khrod gsal bar mdzad //
NK041(di)037:133: pas na de'i rjes su zhugs /
NK041(di)037:134: rtag chad mthar lta'i g.yangs su ma lhung zhing //
NK041(di)037:135: bden gnyis zung 'jug lta ba'i them skas la 'dzegs nas //
NK041(di)037:136: nges don chos sku'i khang bzang bgrod pa yi //
NK041(di)037:137: 'khor lo bar pa'i dngos bstan lam rim de //
NK041(di)037:138: rgya gar yul du 'phags mchog klu yis bkral //
NK041(di)037:139: legs ldan 'byed dang sangs rgyas bskyangs gnyis kyis //
NK041(di)037:140: klu sgrub zhabs kyi dgongs pa 'grel tshul las //
NK041(di)037:141: 'phags pa'i yul du thal rang srol gnyis gyes //
NK041(di)037:142: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir thams cad mkhyen pa rngog lo'i
NK041(di)037:143: slob ma dpal ldan ph+y+wa pa chos kyi seng ge
NK041(di)037:144: 'di la slob ma seng chen brgyad /
NK041(di)037:148: rang rgyud pa rnams de'i rjes su zhugs /
NK041(di)037:150: rang rgyud mkhas pa'i srol chen dar bar mdzad //
NK041(di)037:151: bsnyengs bral zla ba'i legs bshad ma nyams pa //
NK041(di)037:152: gang babs bshad srol phul phyin pa tshab lugs //
NK041(di)037:153: lo ts+aa ba nyi ma grags pa la slob ma /
NK041(di)037:154: tshig la mkhas pa gang pa she'u /
NK041(di)037:155: don la mkhas pa gtsang pa 'bre skur /
NK041(di)037:156: gnyis ka la mkhas pa rma bya zhang brtson /
NK041(di)037:157: gnyis ka la mi mkhas pa zhang thag sag pa ste pa tshab bu bzhir grags pa byung /
NK041(di)037:158: thal 'gyur ba'i srol 'dzin pa rnams de'i rjes su zhugs /
NK041(di)037:159: klu sgrub dgongs pa sa gsum 'phags pa yi //
NK041(di)037:160: rig pas bkral ba'i legs bshad bdud rtsi'i rgyun //
NK041(di)037:161: grub pa'i dbang phyug dpal ldan chos skyong dang //
NK041(di)037:162: 'jam dbyangs rnam 'phrul sa chen thugs mtshor babs //
NK041(di)037:163: gzung ba'i chos kun nam yang yod min cing //
NK041(di)037:164: 'dzin byed shes pa'ang 'khrul par gdon mi za //
NK041(di)037:165: gnyis med ye shes sbyang gzhir bzhag pa ste //
NK041(di)037:166: 'khor lo tha ma'i lam gyi rim pa'o //
NK041(di)037:167: mi pham mgon dang klu sgrub snying po yis //
NK041(di)037:168: byams pa'i chos bzhi mdo sde rgyan /
NK041(di)037:171: dbus mtha' rnam 'byed bstod tshogs gzhung gis bkral //
NK041(di)037:172: thogs med mched kyi gsung rab nyi 'od kyis //
NK041(di)037:173: 'khor lo tha ma'i nges don cher cher gsal //
NK041(di)037:174: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir mi pham rgyal ba dang //
NK041(di)037:175: thogs med mched kyi gzhung bzang ngo mtshar can //
NK041(di)037:176: dbu sems so sor 'grel byed rnam mang yang //
NK041(di)037:177: gang de dbu ma'i gzhung du gdon mi za //
NK041(di)037:178: chos mngon pa 'og ma rgya mtsho lta bu'i bka'
NK041(di)037:179: babs 'ban dkon mchog rdo rje rog chos kyi brtson
NK041(di)037:180: 'grus tho gar gnam ldems kun dga' rdo rje /
NK041(di)037:181: byams chos gzhung gi nges don 'grel pa la //
NK041(di)037:182: bshad dang sgrub pa'i bka' babs rnam pa gnyis //
NK041(di)037:183: de dag rim bzhin rngog blo ldan shes rab dang btsan kha bo che gnyis la babs //
NK041(di)037:184: thos bsam sgom pas so sor khyad par 'phags //
NK041(di)037:185: chos kun rig pa'i lam nas legs drangs te //
NK041(di)037:186: gnas skabs gsung rab kun la blta ba'i mig /
NK041(di)037:187: mthar thug kun mkhyen sgrub pa'i lam gyi srol //
NK041(di)037:188: slob dpon phyogs kyi glang po dang de'i slob ma
NK041(di)037:189: rgol ba dbang phyug sde'i slob ma chos kyi grags
NK041(di)037:190: pa'i ring lugs bla na med //
NK041(di)037:191: 'phags pa'i yul du sde bdun rnam 'grel /
NK041(di)037:193: rigs thig ste gtso bo gsum dang /
NK041(di)037:197: rtsod pa'i rig pa ste yan lag gi bstan bcos bzhi'o //
NK041(di)037:199: lha sh+aaka bram ze rgyan dang chos mchog sogs //
NK041(di)037:200: chos grags slob ma kun mkhyen lha dbang blo /
NK041(di)037:201: de'i slob ma sh+aakya blo gros /
NK041(di)037:202: gzhan yang bram ze bde byed dga' ba /
NK041(di)037:203: rgyan mkhan po sher 'byung sbas pa /
NK041(di)037:204: slob dpon chos mchog gam pan chen rgyal rnga bdun pa sogs so //
NK041(di)037:205: la la don nyung tshig gi phreng ba dang //
NK041(di)037:206: 'ga' zhig dpyod ldan mkhas pas byas pa'ang yod //
NK041(di)037:207: ngo bo nyid med rngog lo rnal 'byor spyod pa sa pan dang //
NK041(di)037:208: 'jig rten grags sde'i phyis byon dbu mar 'grel pa yi //
NK041(di)037:209: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir bshad srol rnam pa gsum //
NK041(di)037:210: kun las khyad 'phags sa skya pa yi lugs //
NK041(di)037:211: sa skya pan chen la slob ma shar nub gung gsum /
NK041(di)037:214: tshad ma'i srol de'i rjes su zhugs /
NK041(di)037:215: sde snod mang thos grags ldan mkhas rnams kyang //
NK041(di)037:216: legs sbyar mi shes 'phags yul mkhas pa'i gzhung //
NK041(di)037:217: rang bzhin rkyen dang rnam dbye'i 'jug tshul sogs //
NK041(di)037:218: gang 'chad de la su zhig yid rton byed //
NK041(di)037:219: rgyal ba'i bka' dang dgongs 'grel bstan bcos la //
NK041(di)037:220: rnam dpyod brtson pas thos pa'i pha mthar son //
NK041(di)037:221: tha snyad gtsug lag smra mkhas blo ldan de //
NK041(di)037:222: gzur gnas mkhas mang tshogs pa'i mdun sar mdzes //
NK041(di)037:223: sgra snyan bzo gso sgra tshad nang rig pa rnams la rig gnas che ba lnga dang /
NK041(di)037:224: skar rtsis snyan ngag sdeb sbyor mngon brjod zlos gar rnams la chung ba lnga zhes grags so //
NK041(di)037:225: sdeb sbyor zlos gar mngon brjod sogs //
NK041(di)037:226: tha snyad gtsug lag nyan dang 'chad 'dod na //
NK041(di)037:227: skad gnyis smra ba'i gtsug rgyan shangs ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang //
NK041(di)037:228: dpang lo ts+aa blo gros brtan pa gsum pa'i bshad srol rmad du byung //
NK041(di)037:229: rgyu gzhi rgyud lam thabs rgyud 'bras bu mi 'phrog rgyud gsum gtan dbabs nas //
NK041(di)037:230: sbyor 1 dang dkyil 'khor 2dang las 3 rgyal mchog
NK041(di)037:231: rnam gnyis rdzogs rim 'phags lugs la rim pa lnga
NK041(di)037:244: ye shes zhabs lugs la thig le bzhi ste /
NK041(di)037:245: dga' ba'i ye shes kyi dbang du byas nas snying ga'i thig le /
NK041(di)037:246: mchog dag'i ye shes kyi dbang du byas nas nor bur /
NK041(di)037:248: dga' bral gyi ye shes kyi dbang du byas nas gnas bzhir sprul pa'i thig le /
NK041(di)037:249: lhan cig skyes dag'i ye shes kyi dbang du byas
NK041(di)037:250: nas snying gar mi shigs pa'i thig le bsgom tshul
NK041(di)037:251: sogs bskyed rdzogs lam bsgom pa //
NK041(di)037:252: dpal ldan 'dus pa'i lam gyi rim pa'o //
NK041(di)037:253: 'dus pa'i rgyud la klu sgrub yab sras dang //
NK041(di)037:254: ye shes zhabs kyis rim par bkral ba la //
NK041(di)037:255: 'phags pa'i yul du 'dus pa 'phags lugs dang //
NK041(di)037:256: ye shes zhabs lugs rgya bod mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK041(di)037:257: bod 'dir 'phags lugs la lo chen 'gos dang mar
NK041(di)037:258: pa lo ts+aa ba chos kyi blo gros rong pa
NK041(di)037:259: 'gar dge chag chos rje dpal dpyal chos bzang dang
NK041(di)037:260: // ye shes zhabs lugs la lo chen rin bzang
NK041(di)037:261: gnyos rdo rje bla ma dang rwa rdo rje grags
NK041(di)037:262: // lugs sogs // gangs can 'dir yang 'dus pa'i srol rnams byung //
NK041(di)037:263: 'gos lo'i ts+aa ba khug ba lhas btsas lugs bzang
NK041(di)037:264: brgyud 'dzin gyi slob ma rgyud kyi ka ba tshugs
NK041(di)037:265: pa bzhi / man ngag gi gdung ma theg pa brgyad /
NK041(di)037:266: las tshogs dang phrin las la mkhas pa dral phyam gshibs pa ltar dpag tu med pa yod do //
NK041(di)037:268: phyi nang rang lus dkyil 'khor lha yi tshogs //
NK041(di)037:269: rtsa yig bdud rtsi dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma //
NK041(di)037:270: rim pa lnga dang bde mchog l+au hi pa'i rdzogs rim la /
NK041(di)037:271: rdo rje sems dpa' bsdu ba /
NK041(di)037:273: thig le bsdu ba ste bsdu ba gsum sogs dang /
NK041(di)037:279: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rim pa ste lnga'o //
NK041(di)037:280: rim bzhi'i rnal 'byor ni nag po pa'i lugs te /
NK041(di)037:281: shes bya rgyud kyi rim pa /
NK041(di)037:282: nyams len sngags kyi rim pa /
NK041(di)037:283: ye shes skye ba'i rim pa /
NK041(di)037:286: 'khor lo sdom pa'i lam gyi rim pa'o //
NK041(di)037:287: rnal 'byor gsang mtha' 'khor lo bde mchog rgyud //
NK041(di)037:288: l+au hi pa dang grub chen dril bu pa //
NK041(di)037:289: nag po'i zhabs kyis rim par bkral ba las //
NK041(di)037:290: 'phags pa'i yul du l+au dril nag gsum lugs //
NK041(di)037:291: grub chen mal dang mar pa do pa chos kyi
NK041(di)037:292: dbang po pu hrang pa lo chung grags mchog shes
NK041(di)037:293: rab / rong pa 'gar dge g.yag sde lo ts+aa
NK041(di)037:294: ba bsod nams bzang po rnam gnyis sbal sna sbal
NK041(di)037:295: spang sna ba'i lugs la sogs //
NK041(di)037:296: bde mchog srol rnams bod yul ljongs su babs /
NK041(di)037:297: rje btsun mal gyo lo ts+aa ba blo gros grags pa gyis gzhung bsgyur gtan la phabs //
NK041(di)037:298: rgyur rgyu rigs spang bya rkyen la ltos pa gnas
NK041(di)037:299: spyod dang skyabs sems gso sbyong gtan khrims lta ba
NK041(di)037:300: grub mtha' bzhi'i rgyud sde bzhir //
NK041(di)037:301: rim zhugs smin byed lta ba bskyed rdzogs spyod dang
NK041(di)037:302: nye rgyu mchog thun bzlas dang gtong ma sbyin sreg
NK041(di)037:303: rab gnas las tshogs rab 'byams mngon rtogs dang //
NK041(di)037:304: grogs dam tshig dang sdom pa bcas gnas skabs dang
NK041(di)037:305: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rnam gnyis la sbyor ba
NK041(di)037:306: // dgyes pa rdo rje'i lam gyi rim pa'o //
NK041(di)037:307: dgyes rdor rgyud la mtsho skyes nag po pa //
NK041(di)037:308: mi thub zla ba rin chen 'byung gnas dang //
NK041(di)037:309: n+aa ro pa dang mee tri'i lugs rnams te //
NK041(di)037:310: 'phags pa'i yul du dgyes rdor srol chen drug dang /
NK041(di)037:311: kha che snyan grags bzang po'i lugs te lugs srol yongs su rdzogs pa bdun du'ang bzhed la /
NK041(di)037:312: spyir 'grel byed ni rdo rje snying po sogs bcu gnyis byung bar grags so //
NK041(di)037:313: 'brog mi lo ts+aa ba sh+aakya ye shes 'gos kyi
NK041(di)037:314: gyo zla ba'i 'od zer mar pa chos kyi blo
NK041(di)037:315: gros dpyal kun dga' rdo rje rams lding ma ba
NK041(di)037:318: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir bshad srol rnam mang yang //
NK041(di)037:319: snga ma gsum ga ya d+h+aa ra dang /
NK041(di)037:320: phyi ma n+aa ro pa'i brgyud 'dzin no //
NK041(di)037:321: 'brog mi'i lugs bzang dpal ldan sa skya pas //
NK041(di)037:322: bshad dang sgrub pa'i rgyal mtshan rtse la bkod //
NK041(di)037:323: phyi 'jig rten khams 1dang nang lus 2rnam dag dang //
NK041(di)037:324: gzhan byis pa 'jug pa'i dbang bdun /
NK041(di)037:325: gong ma bzhi bcas bcu gcig dbang 3bskur bskyed rim gyis thun mong dngos grub dang /
NK041(di)037:326: rdzogs rim gyis lam mchog 5dngos grub tshe 'dir sgrub byed pa //
NK041(di)037:327: dpal ldan dus 'khor lam gyi rim pa'o //
NK041(di)037:328: gong gi don tshan lnga po dus 'khor bsdus rgyud le'u lngas rim par ston /
NK041(di)037:329: thabs shes gnyis med dus kyi 'khor lo'i rgyud //
NK041(di)037:330: zla bzang la sogs sprul pa'i chos rgyal bdun ni /
NK041(di)037:332: zla bzang lha dbang gzi brjid can //
NK041(di)037:333: zla bas byin dang lha'i dbang phyug /
NK041(di)037:334: sna tshogs gzugs dang lha dbang ldan //
NK041(di)037:336: 'jam dpal grags sogs rigs ldan dpe gcig la /
NK041(di)037:337: zla bzang la sogs sprul pa'i chos rgyal drug /
NK041(di)037:338: pad+ma dkar sogs rigs ldan nyer lnga dang //
NK041(di)037:342: grags pa rigs ldan rigs kyang ste //
NK041(di)037:343: de nas rigs ldan pad+ma dkar //
NK041(di)037:344: bzang po rigs ldan gsum pa ste //
NK041(di)037:345: de bzhin bzhi pa rnam rgyal lo //
NK041(di)037:346: bshes gnyen bzang po rin chen phyag /
NK041(di)037:348: nyi ma grags dang shin tu bzang //
NK041(di)037:349: rgya mtsho rnam rgyal rgyal dka' dang //
NK041(di)037:350: rigs ldan nyi ma bcu gnyis pa //
NK041(di)037:351: sna tshogs gzugs dang zla ba'i 'od //
NK041(di)037:352: mtha' yas dang ni sa skyong dang //
NK041(di)037:353: dpal skyong seng ge rnam par gnon //
NK041(di)037:354: stobs po che dang ma 'gags pa //
NK041(di)037:355: mi yi seng ge dbang phyug che //
NK041(di)037:356: mtha' yas rnam rgyal rigs ldan dang //
NK041(di)037:357: grags pa rigs ldan de nas slar //
NK041(di)037:358: de sras 'khor lo chen po can //
NK041(di)037:360: smra mkhas rta mchog ting 'dzin gyis //
NK041(di)037:361: kla klo'i chos ni mthar byed pa'o //
NK041(di)037:364: dus zhabs pa dang tsi lu pan chen gyis //
NK041(di)037:365: snga ma rnams kyis sham+b+ha la dang phyi ma gnyis kyis 'phags pa'i yul du spel //
NK041(di)037:366: gyi gyo lo ts+aa ba zla ba'i 'od zer /
NK041(di)037:367: r+ts+wa dang mi bsod snyoms pa sangs rgyas grags dang
NK041(di)037:368: rwa chos rab 'bro shes rab grags rnam pa gnyis
NK041(di)037:369: // chag chos rje dpal dpyal kun dga' rdo rje rong pa rgwa lo rnam rgyal rdo rje /
NK041(di)037:370: jo nang pa zhal lu bu ston rin po che lugs sogs kyis //
NK041(di)037:371: lugs srol mtha' yas pa ste /
NK041(di)037:372: bsdus rgyud rtsa 'grel kho na la'ang 'gyur 'go nyer lnga tsam byung bas mtshon no //
NK041(di)037:373: gangs can bstan pa'i pad tshal gsal bar mdzad //
NK041(di)037:374: rwa 'bro'i bshad srol nyi zla'i 'od ris can //
NK041(di)037:378: bde mchog mal mar lo gsum /
NK041(di)037:380: dus 'khor rwa 'bro rtsa gsum las gtso bor byung
NK041(di)037:381: zhes gzur gnas kyi mkhas pa kun la gtam du
NK041(di)037:382: grags so // slob ma'i dbang lnga sngon du 'gro
NK041(di)037:383: bas slob dpon dbang 6bskur phyir mi ldog pa'i dam
NK041(di)037:385: gsang dkyil du gsang ba'i 'jug pas zhugs shing mthong ba /
NK041(di)037:386: lha dang dkyil 'khor gyi de nyid /
NK041(di)037:387: slob dpon gyi las rim rnams shes par bya ba /
NK041(di)037:388: thun mong ma yin pa'i chos 'chad rjes gnang /
NK041(di)037:389: lung bstan dbugs dbyung gzengs bstod de drug rang rgyud smin byas nas //
NK041(di)037:390: bdag mdun gnyis ka dag pa'i sku ru bskyed //
NK041(di)037:391: ye shes spyan drangs de nyid nga rgyal bzung //
NK041(di)037:392: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi lam gyi rim pa'o //
NK041(di)037:393: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi dgongs pa 'grel pa la //
NK041(di)037:394: rgya gar du don la mkhas pa sangs rgyas gsang ba tshig la mkhas pa sh+aakya bshes gnyen dang //
NK041(di)037:395: tshig don gnyis ka la mkhas pa yongs rdzogs pan chen kun dga' snying po ste //
NK041(di)037:396: bshes gnyen rnam gsum bstan pa'i rgyan du shar //
NK041(di)037:397: bod yul 'dir dang po'i srol 'byed lo chen brgyud par bcas /
NK041(di)037:398: rin chen bzang po rgya gar du lan gsum byon /
NK041(di)037:399: sku tshe'i stod du lag len kun snying dang /
NK041(di)037:400: bshad pa sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyi lugs ltar mdzad pa la /
NK041(di)037:401: phyis yo ga smad lugs dang /
NK041(di)037:402: sku tshe'i mjug tu bshad pa dang lag len gnyis
NK041(di)037:403: ka kun snying gi lugs kho na mdzad pa las
NK041(di)037:404: yo ga stod lugs su grags pa byung /
NK041(di)037:405: slob ma mang yang thugs sras kyi mchog bzhi ste /
NK041(di)037:406: lo chung legs pa'i shes rab /
NK041(di)037:407: mang nang gi gur shing brtson 'grus rgyal mtshan /
NK041(di)037:408: grwa pa gzhon nu shes rab /
NK041(di)037:409: skyi nor dz+ny+aa na rnams so //
NK041(di)037:410: bar du dar mdzad r+ts+wa skya ba snur nyi ma
NK041(di)037:411: 'od zer 'dzim pa blo chen gsum sogs jo bo
NK041(di)037:412: dang rin bzang gi brgyud 'dzin rnam pa dang //
NK041(di)037:413: tha mar spel mdzad kun mkhyen bu ston rin chen grub //
NK041(di)037:414: gang 'di snyigs dus rgyal ba gnyis pa'o //
NK041(di)037:416: mtha' rten dang bcas pa'i dbang sogs kyis rang rgyud smin byas nas //
NK041(di)037:417: mdun bskyed thugs kar yig 'bru'i sa bon bkod //
NK041(di)037:418: rje dpon lta bur dngos grub len byed pa //
NK041(di)037:419: bya ba'i rgyud kyi lam gyi rim pa'o //
NK041(di)037:420: bya rgyud kyi dbang rnams kyi steng rdo rje dril bu'i dbang gis smin byas nas //
NK041(di)037:421: bdag mdun gnyis ka'i thugs kar yig 'bru bkod //
NK041(di)037:422: grogs po lta bur dngos grub len byed pa //
NK041(di)037:423: spyod pa'i rgyud kyi lam gyi rim pa'o //
NK041(di)037:424: de lta bu'i bya spyod shing rta'i srol 'byed pa /
NK041(di)037:425: bya rgyud la slob dpon byang chub mchog dang /
NK041(di)037:426: spyod rgyud la slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i bshad srol phun sum tshogs //
NK041(di)037:427: gangs can 'dir yang bya spyod rgyud sde la //
NK041(di)037:428: ngo mtshar bshad pa'i brgyud 'dzin bla ma pa ri
NK041(di)037:429: lo ts+aa ba rin chen grags sogs bgrang yas byon
NK041(di)037:430: // yang rgya gar du phyis jo bo dz+ny+aa na sh+r+ai dang /
NK041(di)037:431: pun+ya sh+r+ai gnyis lung mang bar grags la /
NK041(di)037:432: bod 'dir steng pa lo ts+aa ba tshul khrims 'byung gnas /
NK041(di)037:433: ba ri lo ts+aa ba rin chen grags sogs dang /
NK041(di)037:434: phyis su shabs bag ston gzhon nu tshul khrims kyi
NK041(di)037:435: thugs bskyed dang brtson 'grus kyi mthu phun sum tshogs
NK041(di)037:436: pa la brten nas sde snod rgyud sde dang bcas
NK041(di)037:437: rgyal ba'i bka' 'gyur ro cog yongs su rdzogs pa
NK041(di)037:438: phal mo che'i lung tshang bar bzhugs so //
NK041(di)037:439: 'phags pa'i yul dang gangs ri'i khrod 'dir yang //
NK041(di)037:440: mdo sngags gnyis kyi 'gros chen ma 'khrul pa //
NK041(di)037:441: sngon rab mkhas pas bkral ba'i bshad srol te //
NK041(di)037:442: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi bzhed gzhung yin //
NK041(di)037:443: 'on kyang byang phyogs gangs ri'i khrod 'di ru //
NK041(di)037:444: log pa'i gzhung lugs rnam dag rgyud sde ru //
NK041(di)037:445: mngon zhen dam pos 'bad nas nyan pa dang //
NK041(di)037:446: gzhan la 'chad pa'i mkhas rlom mang zhig byung //
NK041(di)037:447: 'ga' zhig grags 'dod chang gis rab myos nas //
NK041(di)037:448: rgyal ba'i bka' snga 'gyur gyi rgyud lung man ngag dang tshad ldan gzhung rnams dang //
NK041(di)037:449: de dag sgyur byed lo pan pad 'byung bi ma bee ro sogs mkhas rnams la //
NK041(di)037:450: brtsad cing rgol ba'i log rtog mang zhig mthong //
NK041(di)037:451: kha cig 'di na rang bzo'i sbyor ba yis //
NK041(di)037:452: sngon rabs mkhas pas bkral ba'i bshad srol rnams //
NK041(di)037:453: mi mngon nam mkha'i dbyings su rab bcings nas //
NK041(di)037:454: rang 'dod grub mtha'i rgyu skar bgrang yas 'char //
NK041(di)037:455: gsang chen rgyud dang dbu sems shing rta'i srol //
NK041(di)037:456: klu sgrub dgongs pa thal rang srol gnyis kyis //
NK041(di)037:457: legs par bkral ba'i bshad srol zla med pa //
NK041(di)037:458: de dag phal cher 'khyog po'i lam du bkral //
NK041(di)037:459: tshad ldan gzhung bzhin 'chad pa'i mkhas rnams kyis //
NK041(di)037:460: sngon rabs mkhas pa'i bshad srol gzhung bsrangs nas //
NK041(di)037:461: 'chad rtsod rtsom pas thub bstan bzung ba na //
NK041(di)037:462: kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i bstan pa gnyis shig byung //
NK041(di)037:463: nyan bshad thub bstan 'dzin par rloms rnams kyang //
NK041(di)037:464: gzhan gzhung 'jig dang rang gzhung bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK041(di)037:465: khungs med tshig phreng lbu ba'i zol gyis ni //
NK041(di)037:466: rang phyogs 'phyar ba'i rtsod pas thub bstan dkrugs //
NK041(di)037:467: la la rgyal ba'i bka' dang dgongs 'grel gyi //
NK041(di)037:468: tshad ldan gzhung gi nyan bshad kun dor nas //
NK041(di)037:469: rang rang 'dod pas sbyar ba'i gzhung lugs la //
NK041(di)037:470: nyan bshad bgyid pas tshe lo 'da' ba mtshar //
NK041(di)037:471: tshe 'di'i che thabs rnyed bkur lhur blangs nas //
NK041(di)037:472: kha rol brnyas dang phrag dog 'gran sems kyis //
NK041(di)037:473: rang nyid bsgom dang gzhan la 'doms kyang rung //
NK041(di)037:474: sgo gsum bya ba phal cher don med yin //
NK041(di)037:475: de phyir blo gsal klog pa lhur len rnams //
NK041(di)037:476: rang gzhan grub mtha'i rnam dbye legs rtogs nas //
NK041(di)037:477: sngar bshad mkhas pas bkral ba'i bshad srol la //
NK041(di)037:478: rnam dpyod brtson pas thos pa'i pha mthar skyol //
NK041(di)037:479: rig pa'i gnas la thos bsam mthar phyin nas //
NK041(di)037:480: thos pa'i don rnams don yod bya ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)037:481: ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i bya ba lhur blangs nas //
NK041(di)037:482: dben pa'i gnas su rang rgyud smin par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:483: rang rgyud smin nas 'khor mang dbus su ni //
NK041(di)037:484: dri med gzhung la rig grol spobs pa yis //
NK041(di)037:485: rtsod rtsom mkhas pa'i bya ba rnam gsum gyis //
NK041(di)037:486: gcig tu bstan pa 'ba' zhig lhag par dgongs //
NK041(di)037:487: 'chad pa rna ba'i bdud rtsi lha yi dbyangs //
NK041(di)037:488: 'jigs med spobs pa mi zad chu bo'i rgyun //
NK041(di)037:489: rtsom phreng thub bstan mdzes pa'i khang bzang rgyan //
NK041(di)037:490: de dag gsum gyis gzhan la 'doms par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:492: bsgrub dang sun 'byin tsher ma dbyung la mkhas //
NK041(di)037:493: sgra gnas brgyad ni ji skad du /
NK041(di)037:494: sgra skad ming dang mtshan ma dang //
NK041(di)037:495: brda dang tha snyad tshig don brgyad //
NK041(di)037:498: zin pa'i sgra sems can du ston pa'o //
NK041(di)037:502: mngon pa'i lugs kyis yi ge 'dus pa dang /
NK041(di)037:503: brda sprod pas byings la rkyen sbyar zhing rnam dbye ma sbyar ba'o //
NK041(di)037:505: ming des mtshon par byed pa'o //
NK041(di)037:507: tha snyad sngar med pa la glo bur du 'dod pas sbyar ba ste /
NK041(di)037:508: yal ga dang lo ma ldan pa'i ming la shing zhes btags pas /
NK041(di)037:509: ming ming can du 'brel bar go ba lta bu'o //
NK041(di)037:511: de nyid la 'jug ldog byed pa'i phyir brjod pa ste /
NK041(di)037:512: gdung 'degs nus pa'i shing la ka ba zhes btags pa lta bu'o //
NK041(di)037:514: mngon pa'i lugs kyi ming 'dus pa dang /
NK041(di)037:515: brda sprod pa byings dang ming la ting supa kyi rkyen sbyar ba la 'dod do //
NK041(di)037:517: chos gang zhig rang rang gi gnas lugs ji ltar gnas pa ste /
NK041(di)037:518: me'i ngo bo tsha ba lta bu'o //
NK041(di)037:519: kyi tshig sbyor kun tshang ba'i //
NK041(di)037:520: 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'ang de ltar tshims par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:521: ne tso'i 'don pas mkhas par rlom pa dang //
NK041(di)037:522: tshul 'chos spyod pas btsun par 'chos pa dang //
NK041(di)037:523: stong pa'i 'ud kyis bzang por bardzu ba yi //
NK041(di)037:524: klog pa ba de 'jig rten sgyu ma mkhan //
NK041(di)037:525: 'gro kun srid pa'i mtsho las bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)037:526: gcig tu bstan pa 'ba' zhig nyer dgongs nas //
NK041(di)037:527: rnam dag gzhung lugs nyan dang 'chad pa yi //
NK041(di)037:528: klog pa ba de lha mi'i mchod gnas yin //
NK041(di)037:529: mdor na sngon rabs mkhas pa'i bshad srol la //
NK041(di)037:530: nyan bshad mdzod dang phyogs kyi bshes gnyen rnams //
NK041(di)037:531: lus kyis thal sbyar ngag gis bstod pa dang //
NK041(di)037:532: yid kyi rjes su yi rangs lan brgyar bsgom //
NK041(di)037:533: la lar mdo dang 'ga' zhig sngags gzhung tsam //
NK041(di)037:534: gzhan dag sgra tshad tsam zhes phyogs re'i mig /
NK041(di)037:535: phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba rat+na'i zhabs //
NK041(di)037:536: rig gnas kun la spobs pa dge ba can //
NK041(di)037:537: sa gsum 'gran zla bral ba chos kyi rje //
NK041(di)037:538: khyod gsung lan brgyar myong ba'i bsod snyoms pas //
NK041(di)037:539: kun nas mdangs sdug nags kyi sman ljongs na //
NK041(di)037:540: bla ma dam pa'i yon tan rjes su dran //
NK041(di)037:541: 'ga' zhig log pa'i gzhung lugs dag par 'chad //
NK041(di)037:542: kha cig rnam dag gzhung lugs log par blta //
NK041(di)037:543: de phyir de dag kun la snyan bskul du //
NK041(di)037:544: cung zad zhus mod thugs kyis bzod par gsol //
NK041(di)037:545: 'di bsrings dge bas bdag kyang phyi ma'i dus //
NK041(di)037:546: dam pas rjes bzung rnam dang gzhung lugs la //
NK041(di)037:547: nyan dang bshad dang klog pa lhur blangs nas //
NK041(di)037:548: thos dang bsam pas bshad rgyun 'dzin par shog /
NK041(di)037:549: gang 'di rgya bod mkhas pa'i bshad srol rnams //
NK041(di)037:550: mang du thos pa nags kyi klog pa pradz+ny+aa rasmi bas //
NK041(di)037:551: rat+na k+au ta'i sa 'dzin pho brang nas //
NK041(di)037:553: nyan bshad 'dzin pa'i bshes gnyen kun la springs //
NK041(di)037:554: sarba d+aa ka l+y+aa nam b+ha ba tu //
NK041(di)037:555: gangs ri'i khrod kyi spong ba bsam gtan pa rnams
NK041(di)037:556: kyi snyan du bsrings pa bsgom pa 'chi med bdud
NK041(di)037:558: sku bzhi'i dbang phyug dpal rdo rje 'chang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)037:559: skyes bu gsum gyi lam gyis rgyud sbyangs ka dag lhun grub dbyer med ngang /
NK041(di)037:560: bde stong zung 'jug dbang bzhi'i lam bsgom phyag rgya chen por mnyam bzhag pas /
NK041(di)037:561: gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa rang sar zhi ba mchog tu mi 'gyur ye shes kyis //
NK041(di)037:562: rdo rje gsum gyi go 'phang sbyin mkhas khyab bdag bla mas dge legs mdzod //
NK041(di)037:563: rgyal ba'i gsung rab kun gyi snying po'i phul //
NK041(di)037:564: rtogs pa'i dam chos nyams su len 'dod na //
NK041(di)037:565: sum ldan bla ma sangs rgyas dngos su bsgom //
NK041(di)037:566: grub thob gong ma'i snyan brgyud gdams pa la //
NK041(di)037:567: dran 'dun drag pos rtse gcig nyams su longs //
NK041(di)037:568: log pa'i gdams pa nyin mtshan khor yug tu //
NK041(di)037:569: nyams su blangs kyang ngal ba don med pas //
NK041(di)037:570: de phyir grub chen gdams pa 'di yin zhes //
NK041(di)037:571: phyogs kyi sgom chen rnams la 'di bsrings so //
NK041(di)037:572: rgyal bas lung bstan gangs can 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK041(di)037:573: gcig tu bstan pa 'ba' zhig nyer dgongs pa'i //
NK041(di)037:574: sngon gyi chos rgyal ye shes 'od kyang ngo //
NK041(di)037:576: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir ston pa gnyis pa yin //
NK041(di)037:577: zhu chen lo ts+aa pa gor bee ro dang //
NK041(di)037:578: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob 'brom ston u pa s+ai //
NK041(di)037:579: mkhas grub chen po khyung po rnal 'byor pa //
NK041(di)037:580: skad gnyis smra ba bla chen 'brog mi dang //
NK041(di)037:581: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rje btsun mar pa'i zhabs //
NK041(di)037:582: grub pa'i sar bzhugs dam pa rgya gar dang //
NK041(di)037:583: gyi gyo lo ts+aa mkhas grub o rgyan pa //
NK041(di)037:584: byang phyogs sgrub brgyud 'degs pa'i ka chen brgyad //
NK041(di)037:585: dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang nas legs 'ongs pa'i //
NK041(di)037:586: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir sgrub brgyud srol chen brgyad //
NK041(di)037:587: de dag grub thob gong ma'i gshegs shul yin //
NK041(di)037:588: thar 'dod rnams kyang lam de'i rjes su zhugs //
NK041(di)037:589: sems sde tshogs drug yul du snang ba gang shar yang //
NK041(di)037:590: gdod nas grub pa'i gnyug ma'i ye shes te //
NK041(di)037:591: rang zhal blta zhing klong sde bsgom med ma yengs par //
NK041(di)037:592: man ngag sde snang bzhi'i chos nyid mngon sum /
NK041(di)037:596: don la mnyam par 'jog pa nyid //
NK041(di)037:597: rdzogs chen zhes pa'i don ni /
NK041(di)037:598: ma h+aa san+d+hi'i sgra las drangs na yang dag pa'i bsam gtan chen po zhes par 'gyur te /
NK041(di)037:599: theg brgyad blo yi grub mtha' las 'das pa'i gnas
NK041(di)037:600: lugs gcig pu'i klong du 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK041(di)037:601: cad rang shar ba'i ye shes bla na med pa'i
NK041(di)037:603: chos thams cad sems nyid gcig pu'i rol par rgyu
NK041(di)037:604: rkyen rtsol sgrub las 'das par rtogs pas spang bya'i
NK041(di)037:605: mtha' las grol ba phyi sems sde /
NK041(di)037:606: de la'ang nang gses su 'bras bu sems kyi byung sar 'dod pa sogs bdun no //
NK041(di)037:607: chos can thams cad chos nyid kun tu bzang mo'i
NK041(di)037:608: klong las 'gro 'ong med pa'i phyir sku gsum rang
NK041(di)037:609: chas kyi dbyings las mi 'gyur bar rtogs pas gnyen
NK041(di)037:610: po'i mtha' las grol ba nang bya bral klong gi
NK041(di)037:611: sde / de la'ang dkar nag khra gsum rab 'byams kyi klong sde bzhi'o //
NK041(di)037:612: gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi chos thams cad ka dag
NK041(di)037:613: dang lhun grub dbyer med pa'i don rang gi mtshan
NK041(di)037:614: nyid yin lugs ltar rtogs pas spang gnyen gnyis ka'i
NK041(di)037:615: mtha' las grol ba gsang ba zab pa man ngag
NK041(di)037:619: rgyud rang gzhung du bstan pa dang gsum mo //
NK041(di)037:620: de skad du'ang bkod pa chen po las /
NK041(di)037:621: yid can rnams la sems kyi sde //
NK041(di)037:622: nam mkha' can la klong gi sde //
NK041(di)037:623: rim rtsol bral la man ngag go //
NK041(di)037:625: chos kyi nyams len gtso bo yin //
NK041(di)037:626: rten gzhi'i gtso bo rgyud ma h+aa lung a nu man ngag a ti yo ga gsum /
NK041(di)037:627: sh+r+ai seng ha dpal gyi seng ge'i khyad par gdams pa mchog /
NK041(di)037:628: dang por bka' babs sngags 'chang bee ro yis //
NK041(di)037:629: thugs nyams bzhes nas gangs ri'i khrod 'dir spel //
NK041(di)037:631: de yang sems phyogs rnams mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan /
NK041(di)037:632: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po /
NK041(di)037:633: gsang ston ye shes bla ma /
NK041(di)037:635: li za shes rab sgron ma la gsungs pa ste rim pa lngar grags shing /
NK041(di)037:636: bee ro dang g.yu sgra gnyis ka las /
NK041(di)037:637: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ras gsan pa sogs las dang /
NK041(di)037:639: bee ros spang mi pham mgon po la gsungs nas dar ba sogs mtha' yas /
NK041(di)037:640: man ngag gi sde snying thig gi skor ni /
NK041(di)037:643: pan chen bi ma la mi tra /
NK041(di)037:644: des mnga' bdag dang nyang ban sogs la gsungs pa dang /
NK041(di)037:645: slob dpon chen po pad+mas sh+r+ai seng ha la gsan nas /
NK041(di)037:646: mkha' 'gro mtsho rgyal la gdams pa sogs phyis kun
NK041(di)037:647: mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po dri med 'od zer gyi
NK041(di)037:648: bka' drin las rgya cher dar ro //
NK041(di)037:649: rgyus nyang rma dang 'khon zur gnubs myos dang /
NK041(di)037:650: srid rong dpyal dang skyo ston g.yung la sogs //
NK041(di)037:651: snga 'gyur rnying ma'i bka' brgyud bgrang yas byon //
NK041(di)037:652: dpal ldan zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis /
NK041(di)037:655: rog sh+aaka 'byung sogs bla ma mang du bsten /
NK041(di)037:656: mdo sgyu sems gsum la mkhas pa'i phul du byin /
NK041(di)037:657: rtsa rgyud dang bshad rgyud 'grel pa dang sgrub thabs
NK041(di)037:658: lung man ngag so sor phye ste bshad pa la
NK041(di)037:661: sgom chen brgya rtsa brgyad sogs byung ba'i gtso bo ni zur chung shes rab grags pa dang /
NK041(di)037:662: de'i rigs kyi sras sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge ste zur mes dbon gsum du grags /
NK041(di)037:663: 'di rnams kyi ring la gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi
NK041(di)037:664: phrin las nam mkha' dang mnyam par song bas bod
NK041(di)037:665: khams oo d+ai y+aa na'i yul dang mtshungs par glengs
NK041(di)037:666: so // pa rdzogs chen bstan pa'i rgyan //
NK041(di)037:667: dal 'byor rnyed dka' mi rtag 'chi ba dang //
NK041(di)037:668: las 'bras bslu med 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs dang //
NK041(di)037:669: byang chub sems gnyis nan gyis sgom byed pa //
NK041(di)037:670: bka' gdams zhes rgyal ba'i bka' thams cad gang zag
NK041(di)037:671: gcig 'tshang ba'i gdams ngag tu shar ba'i chos kyi
NK041(di)037:672: nyams len gtso bo ni yin //
NK041(di)037:673: gzhung gdams man ngag gsum du grags pa'i /
NK041(di)037:674: gzhung gdams gnyis la lta spyod gtso bor ston pa'i gzhung so sor yod la /
NK041(di)037:675: gnyis ka zung 'brel du ston pa ni byang chub lam gyi sgron ma dang /
NK041(di)037:676: man ngag ni jo bo yab sras kyi gsang chos glegs bam rin po che'o //
NK041(di)037:677: de las lam sgron gyi brjod bya ni /
NK041(di)037:679: chung ngu 'bring dang mchog gyur pa'i //
NK041(di)037:680: skyes bu gsum du shes par bya //
NK041(di)037:681: zhes pa ltar skyes bu gsum gyi lam rim ste /
NK041(di)037:682: de yang skyes bu'i skad dod pu ru sha zhes pa nus ldan la 'jug pas /
NK041(di)037:683: tshe phyi ma phan chad kyi don sgrub nus pa
NK041(di)037:684: zhig la skabs 'dir bstan gyi skyes bu zhes bya
NK041(di)037:685: / de la'ang tshe 'di'i zhen pa log nas phyi
NK041(di)037:686: ma rang nyid kho na 'khor ba de'i ched du
NK041(di)037:687: las 'bras kyi blang dor sgrub nus pa ni skyes
NK041(di)037:689: 'di yi lam gyi dngos gzhir mi rtag pa /
NK041(di)037:693: 'khor ba mtha' dag las zhen pa log nas de
NK041(di)037:694: las thar ba'i ched du lam bslab pa gsum la
NK041(di)037:695: tshul bzhin du bsgrub nus pa ni skyes bu 'bring
NK041(di)037:696: ste / 'di la theg pa'i sgo nas nyan rang gnyis /
NK041(di)037:697: bsgom bya'i sgo nas bden bzhi dang rten 'brel gnyis /
NK041(di)037:698: gang zag gi bdag med rags phra gnyis sogs so //
NK041(di)037:699: srid zhi'i mthar gnyis kar skyon du mthong nas 'gro
NK041(di)037:700: kun sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'god pa'i khur 'khyer
NK041(di)037:701: nus pa ni skyes bu chen po ste /
NK041(di)037:702: 'di la'ang lta ba'i sgo nas dbu sems dang /
NK041(di)037:703: theg pa'i sgo nas mdo sngags gnyis su dbye la /
NK041(di)037:704: lam gyi khyad par sems bskyed pa sngon du 'gro
NK041(di)037:705: bas rgyal sras kyi spyod pa spyi dang bye brag
NK041(di)037:706: la bslab tshul 'bras bu dang bcas pa'o //
NK041(di)037:708: dal 'byor gyi chos skor ni gsum ka'i lam gyi gzhi rten du bzhed do //
NK041(di)037:709: gsang chos glegs bam rin po che'i brjod bya ni /
NK041(di)037:711: skyabs gnas bla ma dran par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:712: lus ni lha yi rang bzhin te /
NK041(di)037:713: ngag ni bzlas brjod rgyun par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:714: 'gro ba ma lus pha mar sogs //
NK041(di)037:715: sems kyi gnas lugs stong par dpyod //
NK041(di)037:716: lnga po 'di yi skya bar nas //
NK041(di)037:717: dge rtsa thams cad dag par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:719: rten gzhi'i gtso bo mngon rtogs rgyan sogs rgya chen spyod pa'i gzhung //
NK041(di)037:720: lha gcig jo bo'i khyad par gdams pa mchog /
NK041(di)037:721: dang por bka' babs rgyal sras 'brom ston rgyal ba'i 'byung gnas kyis //
NK041(di)037:722: thugs nyams bzhes nas gangs ri'i khrod 'dir spel /
NK041(di)037:724: de yang jo bo rje dpal ldan a ti sha'i dus su bstan pa'i dbu brnyes /
NK041(di)037:725: ston pa rin po che'i srol 'byed /
NK041(di)037:726: sku mched gsum gyi ring la dar zhing rgyas /
NK041(di)037:727: glang shar bya yul ba sogs kyi dus shin tu dar ba las /
NK041(di)037:728: pu to ba nas brgyud pa la gzhung pa /
NK041(di)037:729: spyan snga ba nas brgyud pa la gdams ngag pa /
NK041(di)037:730: phu chung ba nas brgyud pa la man ngag pa /
NK041(di)037:731: gung thang nag tsho lo ts+aa bas tshul khrims rgyal
NK041(di)037:732: ba'i slob ma rong pa phyag sor ba nas brgyud
NK041(di)037:733: pa la nag tsho'i bka' brgyud du grags pa'i tshul
NK041(di)037:734: la / bka' gdams gzhung drug skyes 1 tshoms dad pa'i /
NK041(di)037:738: nyams len bden bzhi'i sdug bsngal kun 'byung 'gog pa lam khrid bsdus gdams ngag pa //
NK041(di)037:739: gung thang nag tsho'i bka' brgyud gdams pa 'og /
NK041(di)037:740: bshad sgrub chu bo gnyis ldan gzhung pa mchog /
NK041(di)037:741: sdong po lta bu thabs lam bde drod rang 'bar /
NK041(di)037:742: sgyu lus chags sdang rang grol /
NK041(di)037:746: bar do rgyal ba longs sku ste chos drug yal ga phyag rgya chen po ga'u ma //
NK041(di)037:747: lo ma snang ba la brten nas bla ma /
NK041(di)037:749: sgyu ma lam du khyer ba ste 'phyugs med /
NK041(di)037:750: lam khyer rnam gsum me tog mkha' spyod dkar dmar gnyis //
NK041(di)037:751: 'bras bu lus sems 'chi med sgom rim de //
NK041(di)037:753: khrid chen lngar grags pa'i ni gu'i chos skor rnam pa ni /
NK041(di)037:754: bka' brgyud shangs pa'i nyams len gtso bo yin la /
NK041(di)037:755: gzhan yang su kha'i chos skor rdo rje gdan pa'i chos skor /
NK041(di)037:758: der ma 'dus pa'i man ngag 'thor bu dang bcas
NK041(di)037:759: shangs chos kyi skor bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig
NK041(di)037:760: yod do // de yang bde bas thabs byas pa'i
NK041(di)037:761: stong nyid phyag rgya chen po'i ye shes mngon du
NK041(di)037:762: gyur pa ni bsgrub bya'i snying po ste /
NK041(di)037:763: rtsa ba rdo rje'i tshig rkang las /
NK041(di)037:764: lam gyi mchog gyur 'di nyid nyams len rnams //
NK041(di)037:765: gzhan gyi dus min 'adi'am bar ma dor //
NK041(di)037:766: bde stong dbyer med sku gsum rang shar nas //
NK041(di)037:767: rnam par dag pa'i mkha' spyod nyid du 'gro //
NK041(di)037:769: rten gzhi'i gtso bo 'khor lo sdom pa'i rgyud //
NK041(di)037:774: rdo rje 'jigs byed rnams kyang ngo //
NK041(di)037:775: n+aa ro pa'i lcam ye shes mkha' 'gro ni gu ma'i khyad par gdams pa mchog /
NK041(di)037:776: dang por bka' babs sku gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK041(di)037:780: phrin las rdo rje 'jigs mdzad de ye shes dkyil
NK041(di)037:781: 'khor lnga'i ngo bo dang gnyis su med par bzhugs
NK041(di)037:782: pa'i mkhas grub khyung po rnal 'byor brtson 'grus mgon
NK041(di)037:783: yis // thugs nyams bzhes nas gangs ri'i khrod 'dir spel //
NK041(di)037:791: brgyud rim bdun du chig brgyud bka' rgyas btab //
NK041(di)037:792: sangs rgyas ston pas skal ldan yongs la spel //
NK041(di)037:793: dbus shangs 'jag pa tshul khrims mgon dang nyang bsam
NK041(di)037:794: sding pa mkhas btsun gzhon nu grub sogs bka' brgyud
NK041(di)037:795: rnam mang gyes // nyams len rgyun gyi 'dzug legs khyad par 'phags /
NK041(di)037:796: gsung ngag rin po che la tshad ma bzhi dang
NK041(di)037:797: snyan brgyud bzhi'i sgo nas slob ma dkri ba'i tshul
NK041(di)037:799: gzhung shing rgyas pa gzhung ji lta ba bzhin dkri ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK041(di)037:800: rje sa skya pa chen pos /
NK041(di)037:801: snang ba gsum gyis lam gyi gzhi bcas te /
NK041(di)037:802: nyams blangs ma lus rgyud gsum dag gis shes /
NK041(di)037:804: lam gyi gzhi bca' phar phyin dang thun mong ba
NK041(di)037:805: snang ba gsum gyis rgyud spyangs pa sngon du 'gro
NK041(di)037:806: bas / sngags lam thun mong ma yin pa'i thog mar rgyu dus kyi dbang bskur nas /
NK041(di)037:807: gzhi dam tshig la gnas par bya ba dang /
NK041(di)037:808: lam dngos la rgyud gsum las /
NK041(di)037:809: kun gzhi rgyu rgyud la 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi
NK041(di)037:810: lta ba gsal stong zung 'jug tu ngo sprad cing
NK041(di)037:811: bsgom pa dang / lus thabs rgyud la dbang bzhi dang rjes su 'brel ba'i lam bzhi las /
NK041(di)037:812: bum dbang gi lam phyi nang bskyed rim dang /
NK041(di)037:813: lam dus kyi dbang bskur nas de'i don zab mo nyin zhag re la thun bzhir bsgom pa dang /
NK041(di)037:814: gsang dbang gi lam rlung dang gtum mo //
NK041(di)037:815: sher dbang gi lam pho nya'i lam /
NK041(di)037:816: dbang bzhi pa'i lam rdo rje'i rba rlabs te rdzogs
NK041(di)037:817: rim gyi lam gsum bsgoms pas dpe dang don gyi
NK041(di)037:818: ye shes 'dren par byed pa dang /
NK041(di)037:819: 'bras bu sku lnga mngon du 'gyur ba'i tshul sogs
NK041(di)037:820: mdor na lam gyi dus nas 'bras bu thob rung
NK041(di)037:821: du gnas pas gzhi lam 'bras gsum dbyer med pa'i
NK041(di)037:822: don ston pa / lam 'bras chos kyi nyams len gtso bo yin //
NK041(di)037:823: rten gzhi'i gtso bo dgyes pa rdo rje'i rtsa bshad
NK041(di)037:824: kyi rgyud gsum la brten nas sa drug gi bdag
NK041(di)037:825: nyid grub chen bir wa pas shar phyogs nag po
NK041(di)037:826: pa'i don du lam 'bras rdo rje'i tshig rkang mdzad
NK041(di)037:829: 'brom gsum gyis rgya dpe dang bstun nas bsgyur /
NK041(di)037:830: cha gan dang jo nang kun spangs pas rgya dpe
NK041(di)037:831: la ma gtugs par go rim dkrugs pa'i 'gyur bcos
NK041(di)037:832: mdzad pa dang / gzungs kyi dpal ba'i yig char
NK041(di)037:833: pan+di ta r+aa hu la'i 'gyur yang yod par gsungs
NK041(di)037:834: mdzad pa dang / pas / de ltar na 'gyur mgo drug go //
NK041(di)037:835: sprin 'dzin ga ya d+h+aa ra'i khyad par gdams pa mchog /
NK041(di)037:836: dang po bka' babs bla chen 'brog mi yis //
NK041(di)037:837: thugs nyams bzhes nas gangs ri'i khrod 'dir spel //
NK041(di)037:838: gyi gyo 'brom dang zhang ston zhwa ma lugs //
NK041(di)037:839: ko brag mar lam cha gan jo nang lugs //
NK041(di)037:840: dbang rgyal sa lugs lce sgom mtha' rtsa lugs //
NK041(di)037:841: ste gtso che ba'i lugs srol bcu gnyis dang /
NK041(di)037:842: de las 'phros pa'i rnam grangs mi gcig pa bco brgyad du grags te /
NK041(di)037:843: de yang 'brog mi dang gyi 1gyo las brgyud pa gnyis kyi /
NK041(di)037:844: snga ma la 'brog mi'i sras in+d+ra dang rdo rje las brgyud pa'i lam 2'bras /
NK041(di)037:845: thugs kyi sras 'brom ston de pa 3las brgyud pa'i lam 'bras /
NK041(di)037:846: se mkhar chung ba nas 'phel ba la rab 'bring tha gsum las /
NK041(di)037:847: 'bring du thob pa zhwa ma nas 'phel ba la /
NK041(di)037:848: pho rgyud mo rgyud bsres rgyud dang gsum /
NK041(di)037:850: rje kham bu ba nas 'phel ba'i slob brgyud 4dang /
NK041(di)037:851: sras zhwa ma tsan+d+ri nas 'phel ba'i sras 5brgyud de gnyis /
NK041(di)037:856: tshul khrims las 'phel ba'i lugs te gsum /
NK041(di)037:858: zhwa ma pho mo bsres pa dum bu ko brag 9pa'i lugs /
NK041(di)037:859: zhwa ma pho mo gnyis sa lugs dang gsum bsres pas cha gan 10gyi lugs /
NK041(di)037:860: 'brog mi lugs dang gyi gyo lugs bsres pa jo nang kun spangs 11pa'i lugs /
NK041(di)037:861: lam 'bras sbyor drug rdzogs chen gsum bsres pa la stod dbang rgyal gyi lugs /
NK041(di)037:862: rab tu thob pa zhang gi brgyud par /
NK041(di)037:863: sa lugs la snga bu phag gru 13lugs /
NK041(di)037:867: 'brog mi'i jo sras gnyis dang zhang ston mched gnyis
NK041(di)037:868: sde bzhi'i gsung gces pa bsdus pa mang lam zhig
NK041(di)037:869: po'i 17lugs / se ston las tha mar thob pa
NK041(di)037:870: byang chub ye shes kyis zhing phug 18par gdams pa'i
NK041(di)037:871: lugs te bco brgyad po thams cad 'brog mi dang
NK041(di)037:872: po'i 17lugs / / gyi jo'i brgyud 'dzin kho na las byung ba yin la /
NK041(di)037:873: de rnams kyi nang nas phyis su sa lugs dang /
NK041(di)037:874: zhwa lugs gnyis dar rgyas che ba las kyang chos lugs rgya mtsho'i mthar son sa skya pa //
NK041(di)037:875: gang de sgrub brgyud bstan pa'i gtsug gi rgyan //
NK041(di)037:876: phyag rgya chen po zhes pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK041(di)037:877: 'khor 'das thams cad la khyab pa zab gsal gnyis
NK041(di)037:878: su med pa'i ye shes khyad par bdun ldan no
NK041(di)037:880: ma h+aa mu dra'i sgra las drangs na /
NK041(di)037:881: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi chos thams cad 'di las mi 'da' bas phyag rgya dang /
NK041(di)037:882: de las gong du chos gzhan med pas na chen po zhes bya ste gzhi mthun pa'i bsdu ba'o //
NK041(di)037:886: gnas lugs kyi don de nyid rtogs pa rtogs las grol 'khrul gnyis su byung bas na /
NK041(di)037:887: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun de las mi 'da' bas phyag rgya /
NK041(di)037:888: de nyid las gzhan pa'i chos kyi sku zhes btsal du med pas chen po /
NK041(di)037:890: bla ma'i man ngag gis ngo sprad nas nyams su blangs pa'i tshe na'ang /
NK041(di)037:891: shes dang shes bya thams cad de'i gdangs las mi 'da' bas phyag rgya /
NK041(di)037:892: de las gzhan pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ye shes btsal du med pas chen po /
NK041(di)037:894: lam gyis glo bur ba'i dri ma sbyangs pas gzhi'i bzhugs tshul mngon du gyur pa'i skabs /
NK041(di)037:895: sku dang ye shes kyi rnam rol thams cad de las mi 'da' bas phyag rgya /
NK041(di)037:896: mthar thug pa'i go 'phang yin pas chen po'o //
NK041(di)037:897: mdor na snang sems dbyer med lhan cig skyes pa
NK041(di)037:898: yid la mi byed pa phyag rgya chen po'i 'bras
NK041(di)037:899: bu la sbyor ba'i mdo sngags kyi gseng lam khyad
NK041(di)037:900: par can te / rje btsun sgam po pas /
NK041(di)037:901: sems nyid lhan cig skyes pa chos kyi sku /
NK041(di)037:902: snang ba lhan cig skyes pa chos sku'i 'od //
NK041(di)037:903: de phyir snang sems dbyer med lhan cig skyes //
NK041(di)037:905: sems dang rnam rtog chos sku gsum //
NK041(di)037:906: dang po lhan cig skyes pa ste //
NK041(di)037:907: gdams pas gcig tu sbyor ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)037:908: lhan cig skyes sbyor mi zer bas //
NK041(di)037:910: de lta bu'i don nyams su blangs pa'i dus su
NK041(di)037:911: dwangs ma'i shes pa ste tha mal rtsig pa ma
NK041(di)037:912: bcos pa nyid / te lo las /
NK041(di)037:913: kye ho 'di ni rang rig ye shes te //
NK041(di)037:914: ngag tshig las 'das yid kyi spyod yul min //
NK041(di)037:915: te lo nga yis ci yang bsten du med //
NK041(di)037:916: rang gis rang la mtshon te shes par byos //
NK041(di)037:917: zhes gsungs pa ltar gzhi lta ba'i gnas lugs /
NK041(di)037:918: rang ngo shes nas mi 1mno mi bsam 2mi dpyad 3cing //
NK041(di)037:920: ces pa'i tshul gyis ma yengs dran 'dun dang //
NK041(di)037:921: bcas lam bsgoms pas nyams su blang ba ni lam gyi dngos gzhi dang /
NK041(di)037:922: de'i yan lag rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun
NK041(di)037:923: pa'i thabs lam zab mo bsgoms pas lta spyod zung
NK041(di)037:925: de yang rgyud dang 'brel ba'i thabs lam la bka' yang dag pa'i tshad mar /
NK041(di)037:926: gtum mo las kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK041(di)037:927: sgyu ma rmi lam 'od gsal dang //
NK041(di)037:929: zhes gtum mo lam gyi rtsa ba /
NK041(di)037:931: sgyu lus lam gyi srog shing /
NK041(di)037:932: rmi lam lam gyi drod tshad /
NK041(di)037:934: bar do lam gyi blo chod /
NK041(di)037:936: grong 'jug lam gyi chad mthud de chos brgyad dang /
NK041(di)037:937: byin rlabs dang 'brel pa snyan brgyud la /
NK041(di)037:939: grong 'jug ma gtogs chos drug dang /
NK041(di)037:940: gzhan yang 'pho ba bar do'i khongs su bsdus pa'i chos lnga dang /
NK041(di)037:941: 'khor lo bzhi sogs kyi dbang du byas pa'i gtum mo //
NK041(di)037:945: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi chos gnyis su bsdu
NK041(di)037:946: ba sogs bka' brgyud dwags po'i nyams len gtso bo
NK041(di)037:947: yin // rten gzhi'i gtso bo byin rlabs can ma rgyud bde mchog ste //
NK041(di)037:948: bka' babs chu bo bzhi 'dus grub chen tee lo shes rab bzang po'i slob ma /
NK041(di)037:949: byang sgo srung ba'i pan+di ta n+aa ro t+aa pa'i ste mi mchog zhabs sam /
NK041(di)037:950: rtsod med zhabs zhes grags pa khyad par gdams pa mchog /
NK041(di)037:951: dang por bka' babs dgyes mdzad rdo rje mi yi
NK041(di)037:952: dngos snang rje btsun mar pa lo ts+aa ba chos
NK041(di)037:954: thugs nyams bzhes nas gangs ri'i khrod 'dir spel ba las /
NK041(di)037:955: slob ma'i gtso bo mtshur rngog mes gsum gyi bshad pa dang /
NK041(di)037:956: mi las sgrub pa'i srol bzung /
NK041(di)037:957: de'i slob ma nyi zla lta bu dwags po rin po che dang /
NK041(di)037:959: snga ma'i slob ma phag gru'i thugs sras rgyal tsha rin po che dang /
NK041(di)037:960: kun ldan ras chung mched gnyis las 'phel ba'i khro
NK041(di)037:961: phu pa dang gling ras slob ma gtsang pa rgya
NK041(di)037:962: ras ye shes rdo rje las dpal ldan 'brug pa
NK041(di)037:963: dang / dwags po'i slob ma sgom tshul gyi thugs
NK041(di)037:964: sras zhang 'gro ba'i mgon po las tshal pa bka'
NK041(di)037:965: brgyud dwags po'i slob ma spyan ras gzigs kyi sprul
NK041(di)037:966: dang / sku karma pa / dus gsum mkhyen pa las kam tshang bka' brgyud /
NK041(di)037:967: phag gru'i slob ma 'bri gung pa rin chen dpal las 'bri gung bka' brgyud /
NK041(di)037:968: stag lung thang pa bkra shis dpal las stag lung
NK041(di)037:969: bka' brgyud de 'bri stag rnam gnyis skal ldan za
NK041(di)037:970: ra ba ye shes seng ge'i slob ma rgyal ba
NK041(di)037:971: g.ya' bzang ba las g.ya' bzang bka' brgyud /
NK041(di)037:972: bka' brgyud de rnams phal cher gyi 'byung gnas /
NK041(di)037:973: 'gro mgon phag mo gru pa rdo rje rgyal po'i
NK041(di)037:974: gdan sa pa spyan snga rin po che las phag
NK041(di)037:976: mdor na phyag rgya chen po la bshad pa dang /
NK041(di)037:977: nyams len gyi srol gnyis las /
NK041(di)037:986: mnga' ris nag po ste brgyad tsam byung ba las /
NK041(di)037:988: deng sang cher mi snang la /
NK041(di)037:989: phyi ma nyams len sgrub brgyud kyi srol rmad du
NK041(di)037:990: byung ba ni sa gsum mnyam med dwags po'i bka'
NK041(di)037:991: brgyud de / de'i bshad sgrub nyams len gyis //
NK041(di)037:992: gangs can ri su la phal cher mdzes par byas pa las kyang /
NK041(di)037:993: dpal ldan 'brug pa bka' brgyud ni /
NK041(di)037:994: rje rgod tshang pa las stod 'brug gnam gyi skar ma lta bu dang /
NK041(di)037:995: rgyal ba lo ras pa las smad 'brug sa'i dregs pa lta bu byung bas mtshon /
NK041(di)037:998: sprang phyed grub thob ces kun la rlung ltar du
NK041(di)037:999: grags pas brgyud 'dzin chu bo'i gter lta bu ste
NK041(di)037:1000: / de rnams kyi nyams bzhes ni /
NK041(di)037:1001: lta ba gtso bor ston pa gdams ngag phyag rgya chen po /
NK041(di)037:1002: sgom pa gtso bor bton pa gdams ngag n+aa ro chos drug /
NK041(di)037:1003: spyod pa gtso bor bton pa gdams ngag 'byung ba ro snyoms /
NK041(di)037:1004: 'bras bu gtso bor ston pa gdams ngag rten 'brel /
NK041(di)037:1005: kun la gces pa'i gdams ngag lam zab bla sgrub lnga ni gzhung chos lta bu dang /
NK041(di)037:1006: gzhan gdams ngag bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni zur 'debs lta bur mdzad do //
NK041(di)037:1007: spyir bka' brgyud ces pa'i sgra don ni /
NK041(di)037:1008: rje dwags po rin po che bsod nams rin chen
NK041(di)037:1009: gyis dang por bka' gdams pa'i chos kyi bdud rtsi
NK041(di)037:1010: gsol nas / phyis phyag rgya chen po'i brgyud pa
NK041(di)037:1011: rin po che la zhugs nas rtogs pa brnyes pas
NK041(di)037:1012: bka' phyag chu bo gnyis 'dres kyi gzhung bzung ba'i
NK041(di)037:1013: phyir de skad ces brjod do //
NK041(di)037:1014: gzung ba'i chos kun rang rang ngo bos stong //
NK041(di)037:1015: 'dzin pa'i sems kyang spros bral stong pa nyid //
NK041(di)037:1016: spros med ngang nas gsal stong mi g.yo ba //
NK041(di)037:1017: zhi byed chos kyi nyams len gtso bo yin te /
NK041(di)037:1018: de yang spyir lam 'di la dbang po'i rim pas
NK041(di)037:1019: 'khrid tshul bsam gyis mi khyab kyang re zhig gdan
NK041(di)037:1020: rdzogs bdun gyi man ngag ltar na /
NK041(di)037:1021: zab mo brda yi dbang bzhis smin par bya ba sngon du song nas /
NK041(di)037:1022: dbang po rab gzung 'dzin las 'das pa'i gnyug ma'i
NK041(di)037:1023: sems ma bcos pa'i gnas lugs mngon sum du mthong
NK041(di)037:1024: bas cig car du 'tshang rgya bar byed pa dkar
NK041(di)037:1025: 1khrid rig pa gcer mthong gi gnad /
NK041(di)037:1026: 'bring sgo gsum cha mnyam gyi thig le sbyang ba
NK041(di)037:1027: bla ma sku bzhi'i lam rdzogs pas thod rgal du
NK041(di)037:1028: sku bzhir grub pa smar 2khrid mos gus chig chod
NK041(di)037:1029: kyi gnad / tha ma rim 'jug gi lam lnga
NK041(di)037:1030: thob pas nag khrid gdams ngag phra chod pa'i gnad
NK041(di)037:1031: kyi gnad / dang gsum las / phyi ma la'ang /
NK041(di)037:1032: phyi mtshan nyid kyi gdams pa skabs brgyad rtsa ba
NK041(di)037:1033: gcig tu bsdus nas lam lnga gdan gcig tu nyams
NK041(di)037:1034: su blangs pa la brten nas tshogs lam blo sbyong
NK041(di)037:1035: gis lam 3bgrod / pha rgyud g.yo ba'i rlung spar
NK041(di)037:1036: 'dzin gyi lam rim lnga gdan gcig tu rdzogs pa
NK041(di)037:1037: la brten nas sbyor lam dka' thub kyi srang du
NK041(di)037:1038: gis lam 3bgrod / bcug / ma rgyud bde ba
NK041(di)037:1039: nyams kyi gdams ngag phyag rgya bzhi gdan 5rdzogs su
NK041(di)037:1040: bsgom pa la brten nas mthong lam gyis rjes bcad
NK041(di)037:1041: gis lam 3bgrod / bcug / / snying po don
NK041(di)037:1042: gyi gdams pa rnal 'byor bzhi 'am 6ting nge 'dzin
NK041(di)037:1043: bzhi gdan rdzogs su bsgom pa la brten nas sgom
NK041(di)037:1044: lam ro snyoms kyi bogs dbyung /
NK041(di)037:1045: rig pa rang grol gyi gdams pa sbyor ba yan
NK041(di)037:1046: 7lag drug gdan rdzogs su bsgom pa la brten nas
NK041(di)037:1047: mthar phyin bya bral gyi lam thob par bya ba'o
NK041(di)037:1048: // zhi byed ces pa'i sgra don ni /
NK041(di)037:1049: bod du byon pa'i 'khrid tshul phal mo ches slob
NK041(di)037:1050: ma mi dge ba las bzlog tu bcug nas gzod
NK041(di)037:1051: da'i sems rgyud kyi nyon mongs sbyong bar byed pa
NK041(di)037:1052: gtso che la / 'dir ni sngon las kyi dbang gis lus dman pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1053: nad bu can du gyur pa sogs sdug bsngal rnams
NK041(di)037:1054: 'phral 'phral du zhi bar byas nas rnal 'byor la
NK041(di)037:1055: sbyor bzod par byed pas na dam chos sdug bsngal
NK041(di)037:1058: sdug bsngal thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed pa'i sngags //
NK041(di)037:1061: sdug bsngal gsum gyis sdug bsngal zhi //
NK041(di)037:1062: srid gsum mtha' yas grol gsum thob //
NK041(di)037:1063: sgrib pa kun las rnam par grol //
NK041(di)037:1064: mkha' ltar mnyam pa nyid la gnas //
NK041(di)037:1065: zhes sogs gsungs pa la brten nas btags par mdzad cing /
NK041(di)037:1066: ngo bo pha rol tu phyin pa sngags dang rjes
NK041(di)037:1067: su mthun pa zhes mdo rgyud thams cad kyi zab
NK041(di)037:1068: gnad gcig tu dril ba'i gdams pa khyad par can
NK041(di)037:1069: no // rten gzhi'i gtso bo spyi mdo sher phyin rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum sogs dang /
NK041(di)037:1070: sgos mdo chu klung rol pa'i mdo //
NK041(di)037:1071: rgya gar bee t+aa'i yul gyi tsa ra seng ngar
NK041(di)037:1072: 'khrungs pa'i mkhas pa chen po ka ma la sh+ai
NK041(di)037:1073: la'am 'gro ba'i mgon po dam pa sangs rgyas zhes
NK041(di)037:1074: bya ba grub thob pho mo lnga bcu rtsa bzhi
NK041(di)037:1075: las gdams pa zab mo mtha' dag gsan nas rtse
NK041(di)037:1076: gcig tu bsgrub pa la gzhol bas /
NK041(di)037:1077: thugs dam bder gshegs bcu gnyis dang /
NK041(di)037:1078: ngo mtshar mkha' spyod kyi bla ma sum cu rtsa drug sogs kyi zhal gzigs /
NK041(di)037:1079: thun mong gi dngos grub grub pa chen po brgyad dang /
NK041(di)037:1080: mchog gi dngos grub mthong lam chen po'i ye shes
NK041(di)037:1081: brnyes pa de nyid kyi khyad par gdams pa mchog
NK041(di)037:1082: / bod yul 'dir brda dang gsung gis gzhan la
NK041(di)037:1083: gdul bya so so'i dbang po dang 'tshams par snga
NK041(di)037:1084: phyi bar gsum du bstan pa las //
NK041(di)037:1085: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir brgyud pa rim pa gsum //
NK041(di)037:1086: brgyud pa dang po dam pas kha che dz+ny+aa na
NK041(di)037:1087: gu h+ya la zhi byed sgron ma'i skor gsum sogs
NK041(di)037:1088: gan nga zhing / de dang dam pa gnyis kas
NK041(di)037:1089: rje btsun ong po lo ts+aa ba la gnang ba
NK041(di)037:1090: gan nga zhing / dang / dz+ny+aa na gu h+yas pu hrang lo chung la bshad pa sogs dang /
NK041(di)037:1091: brgyud pa bar pa rma chos kyi shes rab la
NK041(di)037:1092: phyag chen skor so chung dge 'dun 'bar la rig
NK041(di)037:1093: pa cer mthong gi man ngag /
NK041(di)037:1094: kam tshul khrims rgyal mtshan la rtog pa lam khyer
NK041(di)037:1095: gdams ngag gnang ba sogs rma so ka gsum phran
NK041(di)037:1097: brgyud pa tha ma dam pa phyar chen la sher
NK041(di)037:1098: phyin bsgom yod bsgom med gnyis su ngo sprad nas
NK041(di)037:1099: cho lu dang / mdo sbyor dang /
NK041(di)037:1100: don sdeb gsum gyis spros pa bcad /
NK041(di)037:1101: dam pa phyar chung la sngags dang phar phyin gnyis med kyi gdams pas ngo sprad de /
NK041(di)037:1102: bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i srang du bcug /
NK041(di)037:1103: badz+ra kro d+ha byin rlabs kyi lam pa yin gsungs nas rtag tu gsol ba 'debs su bcug /
NK041(di)037:1104: byang chub sems dpa' kun dga' ni gang zag rim gyis pa yin gsungs nas /
NK041(di)037:1105: blo sbyong gnang nas dka' thub kyi srang rkyang khug lam lngas bsdus pa la bcug pa ste /
NK041(di)037:1106: sgo ba'i rnal 'byor pa bzhi yis mtshon bu chen bdun gyi lugs dang /
NK041(di)037:1107: ma jo nyi shu rtsa bzhi sogs grub pa'i skyes
NK041(di)037:1108: bu bgrang las 'das pa byon pas so so'i lugs
NK041(di)037:1109: / srol phra mo bsam gyis mi khyab kyang /
NK041(di)037:1110: skye ba lngar dam pas rjes su bzung zhing /
NK041(di)037:1111: nga dang dgongs pa mnyam pa kun dga' yin ces
NK041(di)037:1112: basngagasa pa chig brgyud kyi mnga' bdag dam pa kun
NK041(di)037:1113: dga' zhes thugs sras mchog tu gyur pas gang gis
NK041(di)037:1116: des rog shes rab seng ge sku mched la gnang
NK041(di)037:1117: ba sogs shin tu dar rgyas che bar byung ba
NK041(di)037:1118: ni lugs srol khyad par du 'phags pa zhig yin
NK041(di)037:1119: la / spyir brgyud pa bar pa bka' tha ma dang /
NK041(di)037:1120: brgyud pa tha ma sngags dang gtso bor mthun no //
NK041(di)037:1121: sor sdud bsam gtan stong gzugs 'char ba dang //
NK041(di)037:1122: srog rtsol 'dzin pas srog gnas 'gog par byed //
NK041(di)037:1123: rjes dran ting 'dzin bde chen bskyed pa de //
NK041(di)037:1124: sbyor drug chos kyi nyams len gtso bo yin te /
NK041(di)037:1125: de yang dus 'khor rtsa rgyud las /
NK041(di)037:1126: so sor sdud dang bsam gtan dang //
NK041(di)037:1127: srog rtsol de bzhin 'dzin pa dang //
NK041(di)037:1128: rjes su dran dang ting nge 'dzin //
NK041(di)037:1129: sbyor ba yan lag drug tu 'dod //
NK041(di)037:1131: bsgrub bya ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba gsum dang /
NK041(di)037:1132: sgrub byed sbyor ba yan lag drug yin la /
NK041(di)037:1134: sor bsam gnyis kyis dbu ma sbyangs shing rdo rje'i sku rnam pa thams cad pa sgrub /
NK041(di)037:1135: srog rtsol gyis der ro rkyang gi rlung 'dzud cing /
NK041(di)037:1136: 'dzin pas de brtan par byas pas rdo rje'i gsung rnam pa thams cad pa sgrub /
NK041(di)037:1137: rjes dran gyis phyag rgya la brten nas byang sems
NK041(di)037:1138: bzhu ba de zag bral gyi ngang du bzung ba'i
NK041(di)037:1140: ting 'dzin gyis de nyid kha sbyor te gzugs kyi
NK041(di)037:1141: sku dang dbyer med du byas pas bde stong zung
NK041(di)037:1142: 'jug rdo rje'i thugs rnam pa thams cad bsgrub pa'o
NK041(di)037:1143: // gzhan yang sor bsam gnyis sku rdo rje'i rnal 'byor bsnyen pa'i yan lag /
NK041(di)037:1144: srog 'dzin gnyis gsung rdo rje'i rnal 'byor nyer sgrub kyi yan lag /
NK041(di)037:1145: rjes dran thugs rdo rje'i rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i yan lag /
NK041(di)037:1146: ting nge 'dzin ye shes rdo rje'i rnal 'byor sgrub chen gyi yan lag gam /
NK041(di)037:1147: sor bsam gnyis gzugs sgrub kyi yan lag /
NK041(di)037:1148: srog 'dzin gnyis srog sgrub kyi yan lag /
NK041(di)037:1149: rjes dran bde ba sgrub pa'i yan lag /
NK041(di)037:1150: ting nge 'dzin bde ba sgrub pa'i yan lag ces kyang bya'o //
NK041(di)037:1151: de yang dus zhabs snyan brgyud las /
NK041(di)037:1152: kun la drug drug ces bya ste /
NK041(di)037:1154: yan lag drug po re re la'ang /
NK041(di)037:1157: zhes don tshan drug drug gi sgo nas gtan la
NK041(di)037:1158: 'bebs tshul sogs rgyas par bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi
NK041(di)037:1159: yi rnam gzhag tu bshad pa ltar dang bla ma
NK041(di)037:1163: rjes srung sdom drug ldan zhes pa'i chings kyang mdzad do //
NK041(di)037:1164: rten gzhi'i gtso bo dpal dus kyi 'khor lo rtsa ba'i rgyud stong phrag bcu gnyis pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1165: de las 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa rigs ldan grags pa mnye bar bsdus pa'i rgyud /
NK041(di)037:1166: le'u lnga pa'i bdag nyid 'grel chen dang bcas pa ste /
NK041(di)037:1167: thog mar sprul pa'i rigs ldan rnams kyi sham+b+ha lar dar rgyas su mdzad /
NK041(di)037:1168: de nas 'phags yul du tsi lu pan+di tas spel zhing /
NK041(di)037:1169: de'i slob ma pin+do +aa tsar+ya ste slob dpon bsod snyoms par grags pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1170: de'i slob ma dus zhabs pan chen te /
NK041(di)037:1172: tsi lu pa chung bar yang grags pa des /
NK041(di)037:1173: sprul pa'i rigs ldan las kyang dngos su dbang bshad
NK041(di)037:1174: man ngag mtha' dag gsan nas khyad par gyi gdams
NK041(di)037:1175: pa mchog / 'di rtsal du bton nas 'chad par mdzad pa las /
NK041(di)037:1176: slob ma'i mchog a wa d+d+hu ti pa /
NK041(di)037:1179: na len+d+ra pa ste 'di gsum ka la dus zhabs
NK041(di)037:1180: pa chung bar so sor grags pa sogs mkhas shing
NK041(di)037:1181: dngos grub brnyes pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig
NK041(di)037:1182: byon / bod yul 'dir dang por bka' babs gyi jo lo ts+aa zla ba'i 'od zer yis /
NK041(di)037:1183: dus zhabs pa chung ba sh+r+ai b+ha dra bo d+hi spyan drangs nas rgyud 'grel rdzogs par bsgyur cing /
NK041(di)037:1184: rang gis thugs nyams bzhes nas gangs ri'i khrod 'dir
NK041(di)037:1185: spel ba las slob ma khrom lo ts+aa ba pad+ma
NK041(di)037:1186: 'od zer sogs bu chen bzhir grags pa byung /
NK041(di)037:1187: khrom los bla ma'i gsung zin bris su mdzad pa las brgyud pa'i gyi gyo lugs dang /
NK041(di)037:1188: n+aa lan+d+re pa'i slob ma many+dzu k+airti /
NK041(di)037:1189: de'i slob ma bal po sa man+ta sh+r+ai /
NK041(di)037:1190: de las rwa lo ts+aa ba chos rab kyis gsan pa'i rwa lugs dang /
NK041(di)037:1193: kha che zla gzhon 'bro shes rab grags /
NK041(di)037:1194: sgom pa dkon mchog srung sogs las brgyud pa'i 'bro lugs /
NK041(di)037:1195: n+aa len+d+ra pa'i slob ma rtsa mi bsod snyoms pa sangs rgyas grags nas brgyud pa'i rtsa mi lugs /
NK041(di)037:1196: de'i slob ma se lo ts+aa ba gzhon nu tshul khrims dang /
NK041(di)037:1197: de las gnyos dar ma 'od kyis gsan pa sogs gnyos lugs /
NK041(di)037:1201: bal po'i pan+di ta re ben+d+ra /
NK041(di)037:1202: chag lo chos rje dpal sogs las brgyud chag lo lugs /
NK041(di)037:1205: kha che pan chen sh+aakya sh+r+ai /
NK041(di)037:1206: dpyal chos kyi bzang po sogs las brgyud pa'i pan chen lugs sam dpyal lo lugs /
NK041(di)037:1210: pa rgwa lo rnam rgyal rdo rje sogs las brgyud pa'i rong lugs /
NK041(di)037:1211: ts+aa mi nas khams pa rgwa lo gzhon nu dpal la brgyud pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1212: de nyid kyi zhang tshal pa gnang ba'i tshal lugs /
NK041(di)037:1213: grub chen sh+aa ba ri dbang phyug gis pan chen bi b+h+au ti tsan+d+ra la dngos su bstsal zhing /
NK041(di)037:1214: des ko brag pa bsod nams rgyal mtshan la gnang ba ko brag lugs /
NK041(di)037:1216: a b+h+aa yas gnyan lo dang /
NK041(di)037:1217: rgwa lo gnyis la gsungs shing /
NK041(di)037:1218: de gnyis ka las bla ma 'gos kyis gsan pa sogs 'gos lugs /
NK041(di)037:1220: go lung pa mdo sde dpal /
NK041(di)037:1222: snye mdo kun dga' don grub /
NK041(di)037:1223: rje rang byung pa sogs las brgyud pa kar lugs /
NK041(di)037:1224: grub thob se mo che ba nas /
NK041(di)037:1225: pho dong pa rin chen rtse mo /
NK041(di)037:1226: stag sde ba seng ge rgyal mtshan /
NK041(di)037:1227: de dang go lung pa'i slob ma shong ston lo ts+aa ba rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang /
NK041(di)037:1228: dpang blo gros brtan pa sogs las brgyud pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1229: khams pa rgwa lo nas sa chen la gnang ba'i sa lugs rnams dang /
NK041(di)037:1230: khyad par dus kyi 'khor lo gangs can khrod 'dir
NK041(di)037:1231: shin tu dar bar mdzad pa ni jo zhal gnyis
NK041(di)037:1232: te / de yang sgom pa dkon mchog srung nas /
NK041(di)037:1237: grub thob se mo che ba /
NK041(di)037:1243: kun mkhyen dol bu pa shes rab rgyal mtshan sogs las brgyud pa jo nang lugs dang /
NK041(di)037:1246: bu ston rin chen grub la brgyud pa sogs bu lugs te /
NK041(di)037:1247: lugs 'di gnyis kas dang por rwa pa'i brgyud pa las gsan cing /
NK041(di)037:1248: phyis 'bro lugs la yang dag par zhugs pas gtso bor rwa 'bro'i brgyud pa 'dzin mod /
NK041(di)037:1249: gzhan du sbyor drug mi 'dra ba phal cher gyi bka' babs pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1250: der ma zad lugs srol phran tshegs ni lkog phreng ba'i lugs dang /
NK041(di)037:1251: kun spangs pa'i slob ma la stod dbang rgyal lugs /
NK041(di)037:1252: sogs mang du byon pa ste /
NK041(di)037:1253: mdor na rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul du dus zhabs pa che chung /
NK041(di)037:1258: kha che pan chen gyi lugs sogs dang /
NK041(di)037:1263: ding ri chos grags te sngon byon bzhi /
NK041(di)037:1267: bi b+h+au ti tsan+d+ra ste bar byon bzhi /
NK041(di)037:1268: sha ba ri thog mthar bar gsum /
NK041(di)037:1269: phyis byon rgya gar shar phyogs pat+n+aa ga ri'i pan+di
NK041(di)037:1270: ta chen po nags kyi rin chen las byung bas
NK041(di)037:1271: mtshon de sogs zab lam rmad du byung ba'i 'di
NK041(di)037:1272: gangs can gyi 'dzin mar khyab par shar ba las
NK041(di)037:1273: kyang / rdo rje'i rnal 'byor zab mo'i nyams len
NK041(di)037:1274: chu pho'i rgyun ltar bar ma chad pa dang ldan
NK041(di)037:1275: pa ni kun mkhyen jo nang pa yin te /
NK041(di)037:1276: kun spangs rin po cher byang sems ye sogs kun spangs bu bzhir grags pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1277: kun mkhyen dol bu par kun mkhyen chos grags /
NK041(di)037:1280: ma ti rnam gnyis sogs bstan 'dzin chen po bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig byon nas /
NK041(di)037:1281: slob brgyud mkhas shing sbyor ba yan lag gi rnal
NK041(di)037:1282: 'byor lhur len pa mang pos stod mnga' ris nas
NK041(di)037:1283: bzung dbus gtsang khams gsum gyi ri sul phal cher
NK041(di)037:1284: gang bas nges don gyi bstan pa nyin mo ltar
NK041(di)037:1285: mdzad do // lus rtsa dag par byed pa sku
NK041(di)037:1286: yi rdo rje bsnyen pa'i yan lag lus gnad byed
NK041(di)037:1287: pa'i bcings pa'i rnal 'byor rgyu sor sdud de'i byed
NK041(di)037:1288: mdzad do // las / 'bras bu bsam gtan sde gsum gyi sgo nas gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1289: ngag rlung dag par byed pa gsung gi rdo rje
NK041(di)037:1290: sgrub pa'i yan lag rdor bzlas zhes 'jug ldang gnas
NK041(di)037:1291: gsum 'bru gsum gyi sngags su sbyar ba'i rnal 'byor
NK041(di)037:1292: sngon du 'gro bas rgyu srog rtsol dang /
NK041(di)037:1293: de'i 'bras bu 'dzin pa de gnyis kyi byed las /
NK041(di)037:1294: byed las kyis bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu dang bzhi'i sgo nas gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1295: yid thig le dag par byed pa thugs kyi rdo rje sgrub pa chen po'i yan lag la /
NK041(di)037:1296: 'jig rten pa'i las rdzogs par bstan pa rjes dran dbang po rab gtum mo //
NK041(di)037:1298: tha ma gzhan lus la brten pa gsum /
NK041(di)037:1299: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam rdzogs par bstan pa'i
NK041(di)037:1300: ting nge 'dzin dmigs bcas dang dmigs med kyi bde
NK041(di)037:1301: ba chen po gnyis su med pa rang rig pa'i
NK041(di)037:1302: bde ba la sems rtse gcig tu gnas pas dwangs
NK041(di)037:1303: ma thig le phyi rol du 'pho rgyu thams cad
NK041(di)037:1304: rdo rje nor bu nas phyir 'dzag pa med par
NK041(di)037:1306: grub pa'i slob dpon oo d+ai y+aa na pa las
NK041(di)037:1307: byung ba'i rdo rje gsum gyis bsnyen sgrub ces grags
NK041(di)037:1308: pa'i zab chos kyi chos kyi nyams su len bya'i
NK041(di)037:1311: khyod kyi lus sems lta bu dang /
NK041(di)037:1313: sems tshig tu brjod pa lta bur bskyed cig /
NK041(di)037:1314: ces gzhi dus su rdo rje gsum mi phyed pa'i 'brel bkod nas /
NK041(di)037:1315: lam dus su rdo rje gsum dbyer med pa'i rnal 'byor bsgoms pas /
NK041(di)037:1316: 'bras dus su gsang ba gsum gyi bdag nyid mngon du byed pa'i gdams ngag khyad par te /
NK041(di)037:1318: rtsa sbyangs pas ni lus kyi dri ma dag /
NK041(di)037:1319: rlung sbyangs pas ni ngag gi dri ma dag /
NK041(di)037:1320: 'dzag med thob pas yid kyi bag chags bcom //
NK041(di)037:1321: 'khor lo'i mdud pa dga' bzhi'i 'gros kyis bshig /
NK041(di)037:1322: ma rig gnyid ni brgyal ba log pas dwangs //
NK041(di)037:1323: chags bral nyams pa zhe sdang zad pa'i sems //
NK041(di)037:1324: chags pa dag pas bde ba chen por grol //
NK041(di)037:1326: de lta bu'i lam 'di'i rten gzhi'i gtso bo ni ma rgyud bde mchog 'khor lo dang /
NK041(di)037:1327: gnyis su med pa dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i rgyud gnyis la brten nas /
NK041(di)037:1328: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi shes rab stong pa nyid
NK041(di)037:1329: rnam kun mchog ldan ye shes sgyu ma'i gzugs su
NK041(di)037:1330: shar ba'i rje btsun rdo rje rnal 'byor mas legs
NK041(di)037:1331: par bkral ba'i khyad par can gyi gdams pa mchog
NK041(di)037:1332: tu gyur pa / gang zhig dang por bka' babs mkhas grub o rgyan dang //
NK041(di)037:1333: thugs nyams bzhes nas gangs ri'i khrod 'dir spel ba yin te /
NK041(di)037:1334: de yang grub chen rin chen dpal zhes rgyal ba
NK041(di)037:1335: rgod tshang pa'i slob ma brtul zhugs rang dang mnyam
NK041(di)037:1336: par basngagasa pa de nyid mthong lam gyi bden pa
NK041(di)037:1337: mngon sum du gzigs pa spyod pas mthar phyin par
NK041(di)037:1338: bya ba'i phyir dza lan+d+hara sogs gnas chen mang por
NK041(di)037:1339: byon / lhag par oo d+ai y+aa na zhes grags
NK041(di)037:1340: pa rdo rje theg pa'i gan mdzod chen por bzhugs
NK041(di)037:1341: byon / pa / sprul pa'i zhing ye shes kyi
NK041(di)037:1342: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi dga' ba'i tshal chen po
NK041(di)037:1343: der dpal ye shes pa'i zhabs 'bring dang bcas byon
NK041(di)037:1344: byon / pa / pas / yul de'i dbus d+h+au
NK041(di)037:1345: ma tha lar rigs bzhi'i mkha' 'gros byin gyis brlabs
NK041(di)037:1346: byon / pa / pas / / khyad par ka
NK041(di)037:1347: bo ka'i gnas su mkha' spyod rdo rje btsun mo'i
NK041(di)037:1348: zhal nas gdams ngag 'di stsal te skal ldan rnams
NK041(di)037:1349: la rdo rje sems dpa'i gser lam ston pa'i sa
NK041(di)037:1351: gzhan dag las lam bsdus pa sogs rtsa ba dang
NK041(di)037:1352: yan lag gi gdams pa rdzogs par gsan pas mchog
NK041(di)037:1353: dang thun mong gi dngos grub brnyes /
NK041(di)037:1354: bod du byon nas shar gangs su yi dam rdo
NK041(di)037:1355: rje btsun mos snod ldan gyi slob mar lung bstan
NK041(di)037:1356: thob pa / g.ya' bzang pa'i slob ma snubs 'dul ba 'dzin pa'i dbon mkhar chu rin po che /
NK041(di)037:1357: zhes grags pa des gsol ba btab nas mkha' 'gro ma'i bka' rgya grol te /
NK041(di)037:1358: gzhung thog mar yi ger bkod /
NK041(di)037:1359: de nas bzung skal ldan yongs la rgya cher spel ba las /
NK041(di)037:1360: khrid gnyer ba rtogs ldan zla ba seng ge dang dpal ldan sbu tra ba /
NK041(di)037:1362: rnam dpyod mtshungs med rje btsun zur phug pa /
NK041(di)037:1364: gzhan yang rgyal ba rang byung ba /
NK041(di)037:1365: snye mdo thams cad mkhyen pa sku mched /
NK041(di)037:1366: chag lo dbon po sogs mkhas grub mang du byon cing /
NK041(di)037:1367: phyis su nges par thams cad mkhyen pa bu ston rin po che dang /
NK041(di)037:1368: dpal ldan bla ma dam pa bsod nams rgyal mtshan
NK041(di)037:1369: sogs tshad ma'i skyes bu mang pos kyang 'chad nyan
NK041(di)037:1370: bsgom sgrub kyis gtan la phab par mdzad pa'i lam
NK041(di)037:1371: dri ma med pa yin la /
NK041(di)037:1372: slob tshogs rnams kyi nang nas brgyud 'dzin lung bstan
NK041(di)037:1373: thob phyir dang po mkhar chu rin po che las
NK041(di)037:1374: brgyud pa nyid mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK041(di)037:1375: de ltar sgrub brgyud kyi lam srol rnams bka' babs
NK041(di)037:1376: brgyad du bsdus pa de yang gtso che ba dang
NK041(di)037:1377: / lam srol yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang du byas pa yin gyi /
NK041(di)037:1378: gzhan lam srol phran tshegs ni mtha' ma byung /
NK041(di)037:1381: bsnyen sgrub rnams la rdo rje'i tshig rkang rtsod med snang /
NK041(di)037:1382: n+aa ro'i rdo rje'i tshig rkang ni mar pa do
NK041(di)037:1383: pas mdzad par mkhas grub chen po rnams bzhed pas
NK041(di)037:1385: gter byon du grags kyang rgyud sde dang ma 'brel ba dang yi dam lung bstan du /
NK041(di)037:1386: khas len yang rdzun gyi phreng ba bsdebs nas smra
NK041(di)037:1387: ba'i bcos ma'i snyan brgyud du grags pa rnams kyis
NK041(di)037:1388: mtshon / mdor na mkhas grub gong ma'i srol dang mi mthun pa /
NK041(di)037:1389: de dag rdo rje 'chang gi bka' brgyud min //
NK041(di)037:1390: gleng gzhii rim par phye ba ste dang po'o //
NK041(di)037:1391: grol bar 'dod rnams sngon 'gros lus sbyangs nas //
NK041(di)037:1392: dngos gzhi'i lta sgom de yi bogs 'don du //
NK041(di)037:1393: spyod pas nyams blang mthar thug grub pa'i don //
NK041(di)037:1394: 'bras bu thob phyir lam la 'bad par bya //
NK041(di)037:1395: chos kun ye nas med pa'i stong skad kyis //
NK041(di)037:1396: sbyin sogs spyod pa phal cher khyad bsad nas //
NK041(di)037:1397: lta spyod zung du ma 'brel chos lugs shig /
NK041(di)037:1398: sngon dus byung mod dus 'dir sun dbyung zin //
NK041(di)037:1399: spyod pa mchog tu 'dzin pa'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK041(di)037:1400: stong nyid zab mo'i lam la bskur pa 'debs //
NK041(di)037:1401: 'bras bus sku gnyis zung 'jug thob 'dod na //
NK041(di)037:1402: rgyu dus lta spyod zung 'brel nyams su long //
NK041(di)037:1403: dngos gzhi'i dus su stong nyid chos rnams la //
NK041(di)037:1404: stong par 'dzin pa'i rtag 'dzin rtog pa dang /
NK041(di)037:1405: gsal cha dor ba'i 'dzin med lta ba gnyis //
NK041(di)037:1406: mchog 'dzin mang yang mthar lta'i g.yang du lhung //
NK041(di)037:1407: lung rig myong ba'i yid ches bral ba yi //
NK041(di)037:1408: spros bral lta ba'i gya tshoms smra ba dag /
NK041(di)037:1409: rgyu 'bras chos kun stong par blta ba yi //
NK041(di)037:1410: spros bral lta ba tshu rol mdzes pa'ang smra //
NK041(di)037:1411: gang shar sems su sems nyid dang sems snang gi khyad par ma byed do //
NK041(di)037:1413: snod dang bcud kyi 'jig rten ma lus pa //
NK041(di)037:1414: rtag bdag gcig pu bdag gi rang bzhin du //
NK041(di)037:1415: 'dod pa'i mu stegs gsang ba cis mi grol //
NK041(di)037:1416: sgyu mar blta ba mu stegs byed la'ang yod //
NK041(di)037:1417: mthong ba'i lam gyur rnam 'gyur sgyu ma'i dngos //
NK041(di)037:1418: gtso bo'i ngang du rnam 'gyur kun thim pas //
NK041(di)037:1419: de la grangs can lugs kyi thar pa zer //
NK041(di)037:1420: spros bral stong pa cang chad du 'dod pa 'di pa nang pa kho na'i khyad chos min //
NK041(di)037:1421: chos kun gdod nas rang bzhin rnam dag dang //
NK041(di)037:1422: blang bya dor bya'i spros pa kun bral ba //
NK041(di)037:1423: lta ba'i yul du tshangs pa pa yang 'dod //
NK041(di)037:1424: mtha' bral lta ba'ang phyi nang gnyis ka 'dod //
NK041(di)037:1425: rig byed mtha' bral bsgrub pa'i mthun dper ni //
NK041(di)037:1426: rmi lam dri za'i grong khyer 'dzin pa sogs //
NK041(di)037:1427: de 'dra'i rnam bzhag mu stegs rig byed pa'ang byed pa'ang smra //
NK041(di)037:1428: stong pa nyid dang spros kun bral ba dang //
NK041(di)037:1429: gnyis med bde ba zab lam mchog yin zhes //
NK041(di)037:1430: thos chung gang dag mchog tu 'dzin na'ang //
NK041(di)037:1431: dbang phyug pas kyang de kun gsal bar 'dod //
NK041(di)037:1432: rang bzhin ma grub 'dzin med mi rtog cing //
NK041(di)037:1433: cir yang ma grub dwangs la 'gag med pa'i //
NK041(di)037:1434: lta ba'i nyams len zhang zhung bon la'ang yod //
NK041(di)037:1435: lam gnad 'khrul pas grol ba ga la 'byung //
NK041(di)037:1436: bdag med lta ba thal rang lugs so zhes //
NK041(di)037:1437: 'chad byed de dag thos pa'i rna ba bral //
NK041(di)037:1438: de nyid theg chen kho na'i khyad chos min //
NK041(di)037:1439: dngos smra'i gzhung las rang rgyud bden med bshad //
NK041(di)037:1440: gang shar rang sems mdo sems thun mong pa //
NK041(di)037:1441: gzung 'dzin 'gog pa rnam rdzun dbu ma'i lugs //
NK041(di)037:1442: gnyis med ye shes bden grub 'gog pa yi //
NK041(di)037:1443: lta ba'i rnam bzhag dbu ma chen por 'dod //
NK041(di)037:1444: 'dus byas mi rtag phung sogs bdag med du //
NK041(di)037:1445: lta ba'i rim pas 'jig tshogs spong mi nus //
NK041(di)037:1446: 'dzin stangs 'gal phyir ma rig 'joms nus pas //
NK041(di)037:1447: de dag nang nas stong nyid lta ba mchog /
NK041(di)037:1448: man ngag lugs la'ang bdag dang rnam rigs sogs //
