NK041(di)037:1449: phyi nang 'tshol ba'i lag len mang mod kyi //
NK041(di)037:1450: da lta bod na grags pa'i sems 'tshol gcig /
NK041(di)037:1451: bsam gtan dkrog pa'i rnam g.yeng chos su mthong //
NK041(di)037:1452: gang shar sems dang sems nyid rang lus kyi //
NK041(di)037:1453: phyi nang kun la rnam par btsal ba na //
NK041(di)037:1454: btsal bas ma rnyed yul can shes rab sogs //
NK041(di)037:1455: gnas skabs shig tu lta bar 'dod na'ang //
NK041(di)037:1456: blos byas gzung 'dzin spros pa kun bral ba'i //
NK041(di)037:1457: gnyug ma'i ye shes rang ngo 'phrod pa yi //
NK041(di)037:1458: shes pa gsal dwangs rtog med ye shes de //
NK041(di)037:1459: bsgrub rgyud kun gyi bstan pa'i gtso bo yin //
NK041(di)037:1460: rjes thob dus kyi tha snyad de lta na'ang /
NK041(di)037:1461: mnyam bzhag dus su mtha' bral nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK041(di)037:1462: blta bya lta byed sgra rtog 'jug tshul yin //
NK041(di)037:1463: nges pa'i don du chu dang chu rlabs bzhin //
NK041(di)037:1464: lta ba'i rim par phye ba ste gnyis pa'o //
NK041(di)037:1465: rgyud nas bshad pa'i dag bya dag byed dang //
NK041(di)037:1466: zhu ba glus bskul mngon byang lnga la sogs //
NK041(di)037:1467: gtso bo ro ba'i rang bzo'i cho ga yis //
NK041(di)037:1468: bskyed rim bsgom pa mu stegs byed dang mtshungs //
NK041(di)037:1469: rdzogs rim ma zin bskyed rim bzlas brjod kyis //
NK041(di)037:1470: rang lus zhi khro'i lha skur 'char ba dang //
NK041(di)037:1471: ngag gi nus pas dgra bgegs 'joms nus na'ang //
NK041(di)037:1472: 'byung por skye ba'i gleng gzhi mang zhig mthong //
NK041(di)037:1473: bskyed rim dor ba'i rdzogs rim bsgom byed pa //
NK041(di)037:1474: rnal 'byor nang la gzhol bar 'dod na yang //
NK041(di)037:1475: bum dbang bskur ba'i dgos pa'i gtso bo ci //
NK041(di)037:1476: tha mal snang zhen gang zhig bsgom pas sel //
NK041(di)037:1477: kun rdzob snang ba thams cad sor gnas bzhin //
NK041(di)037:1478: gang shar snang ba lha skur ji ltar 'char //
NK041(di)037:1479: ma dag snang ba dam pa rigs brgya ru //
NK041(di)037:1480: legs par rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor ngo mtshar che //
NK041(di)037:1481: des na gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa rab sbyangs nas //
NK041(di)037:1482: gnyis med shes la so so'i cho ga yis //
NK041(di)037:1483: phyi dkyil bsgom pas gang shar lha sku dang //
NK041(di)037:1484: lus dkyil bsgom pas rdzogs rim ye shes 'dren //
NK041(di)037:1485: de yang bskyed rim gzhan stong smra ba'i lugs //
NK041(di)037:1486: rdzogs rim rang stong lugs bzhin shes nas ni //
NK041(di)037:1487: zung 'brel bsgom pa'i theg chen rnal 'byor pa //
NK041(di)037:1488: rdo rje 'dzin pa yongs kyi gtsug rgyan yin //
NK041(di)037:1489: thos sgrogs pa dang mu stegs byed la yang //
NK041(di)037:1490: rlung sbyor yod phyir zab mo'i thabs lam bsgom //
NK041(di)037:1491: rlung sbyor bsgom pa'i sgo gsum bya ba dang //
NK041(di)037:1492: dus sogs 'chugs na bar chad dbang du 'gyur //
NK041(di)037:1493: d+h+au ti'i nang du rlung sna'ang ma chud pa'i //
NK041(di)037:1494: bum chen rlung sbyor bsgom pa ngo mtshar gnas //
NK041(di)037:1495: dwangs ma 'dzag med zhu bde ma brgyan na //
NK041(di)037:1496: drod sogs skyes kyang gtum mo'i dgos pa dor //
NK041(di)037:1497: lus gnad stobs kyis rtsa yig thad du gyur //
NK041(di)037:1498: rlung gi sbyor bas steng 'og bar gsum 'ching //
NK041(di)037:1499: 'byung bzlog rim pas dga' bzhi'i ye shes skye //
NK041(di)037:1500: 'ja' lus mngon gyur gtum mo'i dgongs pa'o //
NK041(di)037:1501: rlung ro dbyung dang rlung sbyor gsum la mkhas //
NK041(di)037:1502: dwangs ma las rlung rang lus dbang du 'dus //
NK041(di)037:1503: lta ba'i rtsis zin thabs shes zung 'brel ba'i //
NK041(di)037:1504: sgom chen de la kun nas rjes yi rangs //
NK041(di)037:1505: 'pho ba'i dus dang gsal 'debs nor ba'ang mthong //
NK041(di)037:1506: phyi dbugs ma chad dus min lha gsod cing //
NK041(di)037:1507: tshogs drug 'gags nas shes pa yul mi 'dzin //
NK041(di)037:1508: 'od gsal thim tshe sbyangs stobs 'pho ba gces //
NK041(di)037:1509: rnam rig mkha' dang stong par blta ba dang //
NK041(di)037:1510: dran tshor 'du shes gsal cha dor ba yi //
NK041(di)037:1511: zhi gnas tsam la'ang zab lam mchog yin zhes //
NK041(di)037:1512: sgom chen 'ga' zhig nan gyis 'jug par mthong //
NK041(di)037:1513: gsal stong rig pa ngar dang mi ldan pa'i //
NK041(di)037:1514: zhi bar gnas mun tshom me tsam dud 'gro'i khrod na'ang mang //
NK041(di)037:1515: zab lam bral ba'i chos kun rnam rig dang /
NK041(di)037:1516: mkha' sogs bsgom pa gzugs med lha la'ang yod //
NK041(di)037:1517: yid byed bral tsam zab lam mchog tu 'dod //
NK041(di)037:1518: gzhan dang ma 'bral de nyid bsgom pa'i 'bras //
NK041(di)037:1519: bskal chen brgyad khrir tshe yi dngos grub 'byung //
NK041(di)037:1520: de phyir lta sgom gnad la mkhas par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:1521: dam pas bkral ba'i lam srol rmad du byung //
NK041(di)037:1522: dpyad dang 'jog pa'i bsgom tshul rnam pa gnyis //
NK041(di)037:1523: rtog dang mi rtog sbyor ba'i dus yin gyi //
NK041(di)037:1524: dngos gzhi'i dus su yid byed bral bar mthun //
NK041(di)037:1525: sbyor ba'i dus su mtshan ma 'byung ba'i gzhi //
NK041(di)037:1526: de nyid dpyad pa'i rten du nges byas nas //
NK041(di)037:1527: mtha' bzhi rnam grol dngos gzhi'i dus su ni //
NK041(di)037:1528: gsal stong 'dzin med sngon rabs mkhas pa'i lugs //
NK041(di)037:1529: dngos gzhi'i bod phyi ma dag /
NK041(di)037:1530: dus su yid byed mi ldan na //
NK041(di)037:1531: dpyod pa sngon btang gnyid log skabs dang mtshungs //
NK041(di)037:1532: des na dus der stong pa nyid do zhes //
NK041(di)037:1533: rtog cing dpyod pa phyis byung mkhas pa'i lugs //
NK041(di)037:1534: rtog dang dpyod kyi blos byas kun dor nas //
NK041(di)037:1535: gnyug ma'i ye shes rang mdangs rjen pa de //
NK041(di)037:1536: bzo med ma yengs slar yang 'phro ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)037:1537: rang zhal blta ba 'jog bsgom lugs yin no //
NK041(di)037:1538: dpyad dang 'jog pa'i bsgom tshul ci yang rung //
NK041(di)037:1539: rang gi mtshan nyid rang bzhin 'od gsal ba //
NK041(di)037:1540: gsal dwangs shar la bsgom med ma yengs pa //
NK041(di)037:1541: sgrub rgyud kun gyi bsgom pa'i gtso bo yin //
NK041(di)037:1542: mnyam bzhag dus kyi nyams len de lta na'ang //
NK041(di)037:1543: rjes thob dus su gang shar snang ba kun //
NK041(di)037:1544: rmi lam sgyu ma'i dran 'dun drag po yis //
NK041(di)037:1545: legs par bsgom na snang stong dbyer med 'char //
NK041(di)037:1546: bde chen 'khor lor pad dkar nyi zla'i steng //
NK041(di)037:1547: rtsa ba'i bla ma gsum ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK041(di)037:1548: sangs rgyas dngos su zhen med mos gus kyis //
NK041(di)037:1549: ma yengs gsol 'debs lam srol kun tu gces //
NK041(di)037:1550: sems nyid ngo sprod tha snyad rnam mang yang //
NK041(di)037:1551: gnyug ma'i ye shes rang zhal bltas pa na //
NK041(di)037:1552: shes pa gsal dwangs zung 'jug ye shes te //
NK041(di)037:1553: rnam dag chos skur kun gyis ngo sprod mdzod //
NK041(di)037:1554: bsam gtan gsum dang bzhi pa'i ting 'dzin dang //
NK041(di)037:1555: gzugs med bzhi la srid pa'i sems rtse gcig /
NK041(di)037:1556: bde gsal stong pa'i mi rtog gol sa yin //
NK041(di)037:1557: lam dang gol sa'i rnam dbye mkhyen par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:1558: sangs rgyas sku dang sha za'i gzugs la sogs //
NK041(di)037:1559: tshogs drug yul du snang ba gang shar yang //
NK041(di)037:1560: gang shar sems dang sems nyid stong pa ru //
NK041(di)037:1561: legs par rtogs na bar chad dngos grub 'gyur //
NK041(di)037:1562: bde gsal mi rtog yul snang gsal mthong dang //
NK041(di)037:1563: mkha' la 'phur dang chu steng bsgrod la sogs //
NK041(di)037:1564: mchog 'dzin mang yang rtogs pas ma zin na //
NK041(di)037:1565: nyams snang sna tshogs dbang po'i gzhu dang mtshungs //
NK041(di)037:1566: sngags rdzas gnyid dang bsgom pa'i stobs sogs kyis //
NK041(di)037:1567: rlung sems 'chol ba'i nyams snang sna tshogs la //
NK041(di)037:1568: mgu ba bskyed pa'i sgom chen mang mod kyi //
NK041(di)037:1569: phal cher g.yeng ba'i g.yang la lhung nyen che //
NK041(di)037:1570: mdor na gang zhig nyams su blangs pa las //
NK041(di)037:1571: dad sogs dge ba ngang gis 'phel 'gyur zhing //
NK041(di)037:1572: chags sogs mi dge ngang gis 'grib gyur na //
NK041(di)037:1573: chos de rgyal ba'i lam bzang rmad du byung //
NK041(di)037:1574: bsgom pa'i rim par phye ba ste gsum pa'o //
NK041(di)037:1575: sdom pa gsum gyi blang dor bslab bya rnams //
NK041(di)037:1576: 'dul ba mdo sde rgyud sde'i lugs bzhin gyis //
NK041(di)037:1577: so thar byang sems sngags kyi bslab bya rnams //
NK041(di)037:1578: spong dang 'khrugs dang rang bzor byed par mthong //
NK041(di)037:1579: chos kun chos nyid shes pa'i 'ud gog gis //
NK041(di)037:1580: lus kyi byed bcing bsam gtan kun spangs nas //
NK041(di)037:1581: phal pa'i spyod pa bag yang sna tshogs pa //
NK041(di)037:1582: 'di ni 'jig rten bslu ba'i kun rdzob yin //
NK041(di)037:1583: chos dbyings rtogs na blang dor mi dgos shing //
NK041(di)037:1584: sdig pa byas na'ang skyon med 'tshang rgya zhes //
NK041(di)037:1585: tho cor spyod dang sha za'i dbang bskur sogs //
NK041(di)037:1586: log pa'i lam la skal med 'jug pa mthong //
NK041(di)037:1587: dpa' bo dpa' mo'i tshogs kyi ston mo sogs //
NK041(di)037:1588: tshogs 'khor bzhir bshad tshogs kyi 'khor lo de //
NK041(di)037:1589: yul chen nyer bzhi'i rnal 'byor pho mo rnams //
NK041(di)037:1590: tshogs la spyod cing bde chen bskyed pa yin //
NK041(di)037:1591: rnal 'byor ming can pho mo sna tshogs pa //
NK041(di)037:1592: 'dod yon zas la mngon zhen drag po yis //
NK041(di)037:1593: tshogs 'khor de ni mi zad 'khor ba'i rgyu //
NK041(di)037:1594: thur sel steng chings dkyil 'khor 'khor lo las //
NK041(di)037:1595: zag med dga' bzhi'i don gyi ye shes 'dren //
NK041(di)037:1596: dbab 'dzin khams kyi 'gros bzhi mi shes par //
NK041(di)037:1597: pho nya'i lam la nye rgyur 'dod pa mtshar //
NK041(di)037:1598: byang chub sems kyis rang rgyud ma brlan par //
NK041(di)037:1599: rnyed bkur bsgrub phyir drag po'i las rnams kyis //
NK041(di)037:1600: 'dre sogs 'dul ba'i tho co'i spyod pa des //
NK041(di)037:1601: gnas skabs grub kyang mthar thug ya nga'i gnas //
NK041(di)037:1602: rgya chen 'dul ba'i gnang bkag khyad bsad nas //
NK041(di)037:1603: mchog tu dregs pa gcer bu'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK041(di)037:1604: grong dang ri khrod tshong dus kun tu rgyu //
NK041(di)037:1605: 'di ni mkha' gos phyi rol pa rnam pa can gyi rnam thar yin //
NK041(di)037:1606: stong pa'i don la yid ches ma rnyed par //
NK041(di)037:1607: rgyus med smra ba'i blun po'i gya tshom gyis //
NK041(di)037:1608: dkar nag las kyi rgyu 'bras khyad bsad pa //
NK041(di)037:1609: 'di ni tshu rol mdzes pa'i lung ngan yin //
NK041(di)037:1610: snang srid thams cad sgyu mar shes pa yis //
NK041(di)037:1611: ci bya lam 'gyur kun spyod ma rtogs par //
NK041(di)037:1612: ngo tsha bor ba'i spyod lam sna tshogs pa //
NK041(di)037:1613: 'di ni mu stegs spyod pa'i nyams len yin //
NK041(di)037:1614: g+ho ta 'bal dang me lnga bsten pa dang //
NK041(di)037:1615: gdung ba brtsams dang 'tsho ba gcod pa sogs //
NK041(di)037:1616: bya daka'i spyod pa mu stegs byed la'ang yod //
NK041(di)037:1617: gang byed spyod pa lam du 'gro bar mdzod //
NK041(di)037:1618: ci yang med dang 'dod chags bral ba dang //
NK041(di)037:1619: skye ba dran dang mkha' la 'phur ba sogs //
NK041(di)037:1620: spyod pa mngon gyur gzhan sde'i ston pa'ang yod //
NK041(di)037:1621: stobs sogs ma 'dres yon tan spyod pa tshol //
NK041(di)037:1622: kun bzang spyod pas dang por drod thob nas //
NK041(di)037:1623: rang gi nyams myong rtogs pa'i bogs 'don du //
NK041(di)037:1624: gsang spyod tshogs dang de dag kun gyi mthar //
NK041(di)037:1625: phyogs las rnam rgyal grub thob gong mas mdzad //
NK041(di)037:1626: lus srog gces 'dzin snying rjes ma zin par //
NK041(di)037:1627: ri sul thang chen rgya mtsho'i 'grams dang ni //
NK041(di)037:1628: dur khrod la sogs nyam nga'i gnas rnams su //
NK041(di)037:1629: gsang ba'i spyod pa dgos med gegs su 'gyur //
NK041(di)037:1630: ci byas lam longs gang shar bsgom pa dang //
NK041(di)037:1631: bzang ngan ro snyoms mngon du ma gyur bar //
NK041(di)037:1632: lus ngag yid kyi bya ba sna tshogs pa'i //
NK041(di)037:1633: tshogs kyi spyod pas rang gzhan las sbyor sogs //
NK041(di)037:1634: gnyis med shes dang brtse chen sbyor ba yis //
NK041(di)037:1635: ci byas don 'gyur mdzad pa ma gtogs par //
NK041(di)037:1636: blang dor bsres pa'i rtsing po'i bya ba yis //
NK041(di)037:1637: mthar thug spyod pa dgos med 'khor ba'i rgyu //
NK041(di)037:1638: kun bzang mthar phyin snying rje chen po yis //
NK041(di)037:1639: rdzu 'phrul mngon shes bde sogs 'byung ba'i thabs //
NK041(di)037:1640: dur khrod sogs su gsang ba'i spyod pa bya //
NK041(di)037:1641: gsang spyod la sogs grub chen rnams kyis mdzad //
NK041(di)037:1642: gsang spyod mthar phyin nyams myong skyes pa'i tshe //
NK041(di)037:1643: rtogs pa'i zla ba rkyen gyis 'grib mi 'grib //
NK041(di)037:1644: mang po'i dbus su tshogs kyi spyod pa bya //
NK041(di)037:1645: o rgyan la sogs grub thob rnams kyis mdzad //
NK041(di)037:1646: ci mdzad thams cad gzhan don 'gyur ba na //
NK041(di)037:1647: yul rnams dbang 'dus sa rnams bgrod pa'i phyir //
NK041(di)037:1648: yul chen nyer bzhir phyogs las rnam rgyal bya //
NK041(di)037:1649: n+aa ro pa sogs grub chen rnams kyis mdzad //
NK041(di)037:1650: spyod pa gsum gyi gnas skabs thams cad du //
NK041(di)037:1651: rgyud sde'i zab lam bla ma'i mos gus dang //
NK041(di)037:1652: zhen pa kun bral snying rje chen po gsum //
NK041(di)037:1653: 'bral med bsten pa spyod pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK041(di)037:1654: spyod pa'i rim par phye ba ste bzhi pa'o //
NK041(di)037:1655: rdzogs chen ston pa kun tu bzang po de //
NK041(di)037:1656: rdo rje 'chang dang gnyis med chos skur 'dod //
NK041(di)037:1657: lung rig bral ba'i snga 'gyur gyi chos 'dzin pa 'ga' zhig phyogs 'dzin rtog pa yis //
NK041(di)037:1658: sangs rgyas sku la bzang ngan dbye ba mtshar //
NK041(di)037:1659: sngar byas mi dge'i rnam smin 'byung ba yi //
NK041(di)037:1660: zas gtsang sras sogs sangs rgyas yod ces zer //
NK041(di)037:1661: drang don mdo la nges don lung du 'khrul //
NK041(di)037:1662: sgrib kun spangs dang las ngan 'byung ba 'gal //
NK041(di)037:1663: yon tan kun ldan rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la //
NK041(di)037:1664: rang rgyud bsdus pa'i ye shes med ces smra //
NK041(di)037:1665: shes bya kun mkhyen ye shes rnam lnga dang //
NK041(di)037:1666: stobs sogs yon tan rang rgyud ldan pa ci //
NK041(di)037:1667: gzhan snang sku yi snang ba mi ston pa'i //
NK041(di)037:1668: yang dag rdzogasapa'i sangs rgyas yod ces grags //
NK041(di)037:1669: tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas mngon par sangs rgyas te //
NK041(di)037:1670: gzhan don sku gnyis smon lam bsod nams mthus //
NK041(di)037:1671: mtshan dpe rab gsal yon tan ldan bzhin du //
NK041(di)037:1672: sgrib gnyis kun ldan sangs rgyas yod ces bzhed //
NK041(di)037:1673: dgongs gzhi dgos sogs rnam dbye ma phyed cing //
NK041(di)037:1674: ma rig mun 'joms stobs sogs dgos pa ci //
NK041(di)037:1675: gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang bcas pa'i //
NK041(di)037:1676: ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes yod ces gsungs //
NK041(di)037:1677: tshogs brgyad gnas gyur zhing kun legs sbyangs nas //
NK041(di)037:1678: ma dag snang ba gang gi mthu las 'char //
NK041(di)037:1679: rang bzhin 'od gsal gnyug ma'i ye shes te //
NK041(di)037:1680: 'og min mthar thug chos dbyings pho brang du //
NK041(di)037:1681: chos kyi sku ru ye nas sangs rgyas kyang //
NK041(di)037:1682: blo bur dri bral longs sku'i ched du 'bad //
NK041(di)037:1683: spang bya'i khyad par 'pho ba'i bag chags te //
NK041(di)037:1684: bde chen ye shes gnyen pos bcoms pa las //
NK041(di)037:1685: yan lag bdun ldan longs sku'i sangs rgyas 'byung //
NK041(di)037:1686: srol chen brgyad kyi 'bras bu'i mthar thug yin //
NK041(di)037:1687: yan lag bdun ldan longs sku brnyes pa na //
NK041(di)037:1688: rang snang ma lus ye shes snang bar 'char //
NK041(di)037:1689: gzhan snang gzugs sku'i rnam rol bgrang yas kyis //
NK041(di)037:1690: yid bzhin nor ltar gzhan don lhun grub mdzad //
NK041(di)037:1691: 'bras bu'i rim par phye ba ste lnga pa'o //
NK041(di)037:1692: chos phung brgyad khri'i yang snying srol chen brgyad //
NK041(di)037:1693: gnas skabs gdul bya'i rim pas 'khrid tshul dang //
NK041(di)037:1694: nyams len gtso bo la sogs so so na'ang //
NK041(di)037:1695: mthar thug lta sgom rnam bzhag gcig tu nges //
NK041(di)037:1696: 'phags pa'i yul dang gangs ri'i khrod 'dir yang //
NK041(di)037:1697: dpyad dang 'jog pa'i 'gros chen ma 'khrul ba //
NK041(di)037:1698: sngon rab grub chen gshegs pa'i lam srol te //
NK041(di)037:1699: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi bsgrod gcig lam //
NK041(di)037:1700: 'on kyang byang phyogs gangs ri'i khrod 'di ru //
NK041(di)037:1701: thabs cha khyad gsod lta ba mchog 'dzin dang //
NK041(di)037:1702: gshe bskur 'debs dang spyod pa mchog 'dzin gyis //
NK041(di)037:1703: phyogs rer lhung ba'i 'khyogs po'i srol gnyis byung //
NK041(di)037:1704: mthar 'dzin lta ba'i chu 'dzin zhags pa yis //
NK041(di)037:1705: nges don nyi ma lha yi lam du bcings //
NK041(di)037:1706: bsgrub rgyud bstan pa phal cher mun pa'i gling //
NK041(di)037:1707: thar 'dod skye bo'i blo gros 'jug pa 'tshol //
NK041(di)037:1708: byang phyogs 'di na thos bral sgom chen 'ga' //
NK041(di)037:1709: chen po rnams la tshad mar grags pa yi //
NK041(di)037:1710: rgyal dang de sras kun mkhyen mkhas rnams kyis //
NK041(di)037:1711: thugs nyams bzhes pa'i nyams len kun dor nas //
NK041(di)037:1712: rten 'brel tshogs pa'i mthong snang snying thig 'od gsal
NK041(di)037:1713: rdo rje snying po'i ngo sprod nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK041(di)037:1714: ma yin pa'i sro ma ra tsa sogs snang ba
NK041(di)037:1715: dgu 'gyur gyi rdzas sbyor sogs dang /
NK041(di)037:1716: phyi rol pa'i spyod tshul dang bsrel ba'i ngo sprod
NK041(di)037:1717: byed pa 'di snying thig zab gnad mtha' dag ldongs
NK041(di)037:1718: par byed pa'o // sna tshogs dang /
NK041(di)037:1719: dbang po bslad pa'i 'od zer phreng ba la //
NK041(di)037:1720: sangs rgyas sku ru ngo sprod bsgom pa mthong //
NK041(di)037:1721: chog shes skye bo nyams len e ma mtshar //
NK041(di)037:1722: rnam dag rig pas 'thad pa ma rnyed cing //
NK041(di)037:1723: rgya chen spyod pa'i nyams len kun dor nas //
NK041(di)037:1724: rten 'brel rdzas la byang chub re ba yi //
NK041(di)037:1725: nyams len de la su zhig yid rton byed //
NK041(di)037:1726: zhang zhung bon dang mu stegs byed la yang //
NK041(di)037:1727: sangs rgyas bstan dang 'dra mtshungs bcos pa yi //
NK041(di)037:1728: rnam bzhag de 'dra shin tu mang ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)037:1729: chos lugs 'ga' zhig dogs pa'i gnas su mthong //
NK041(di)037:1730: 'ga' zhig 'di na 'phags mchog rnam gnyis kyi //
NK041(di)037:1731: rig pas bkral ba'i shing rta'i srol gnyis dang //
NK041(di)037:1732: dpal ldan zla ba'i ring lugs las gzhan pa'i //
NK041(di)037:1733: lta sgom thams cad nor ba'i chos yin lo //
NK041(di)037:1734: rdo rje 'chang dbang rje btsun rnal 'byor mas //
NK041(di)037:1735: skal ldan 'gro la tshul bzhin 'doms pa yi //
NK041(di)037:1736: snyan rgyud phal cher spong ba'i chos tshul la //
NK041(di)037:1737: thar 'dod skye bo rnams kyi bag yod mdzod //
NK041(di)037:1738: dbang bskur byin rlabs ye shes phebs pa dang //
NK041(di)037:1739: rdzogs rim bsgoms dang zab mo'i mos gus kyis //
NK041(di)037:1740: rang gi nyams myong yid ches lta ba de //
NK041(di)037:1741: tshe 'dir sangs rgyas bsgrub pa'i nye lam yin //
NK041(di)037:1742: da dung zab mo'i lam gyi lta ba de //
NK041(di)037:1743: sor rtog shes pa'i dpyad pa dang bral bas //
NK041(di)037:1744: log pa'i lam du mngon zhen mi 'dor bar //
NK041(di)037:1745: rang nyid khas len gzhan la 'doms pa dag /
NK041(di)037:1746: bshad dang bsgrub pa'i chos tshul kun mthong zhing //
NK041(di)037:1747: bsam sbyor dman bas gzhan rgyud mi bsreg par //
NK041(di)037:1748: yid ches lung dang rnam dag rig pa yis //
NK041(di)037:1749: rtsod par 'dod na rtsod pa'i skabs bye zhig /
NK041(di)037:1750: de phyir thar 'dod spong ba lhur len rnams //
NK041(di)037:1751: khyim gyi 'du 'dzi dmyal ba'i me 'obs dang //
NK041(di)037:1752: dgra gnyen bar ma tshong 'dus skye bo'i tshogs //
NK041(di)037:1753: srid pa'i phun tshogs nam mkha'i 'ja' dang mtshungs //
NK041(di)037:1754: de ltar shes nas tshe 'di'i zhen pa spongs //
NK041(di)037:1755: dal 'byor rnyed dka' nges par 'chi ba dang //
NK041(di)037:1756: las 'bras bslu med 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs rnams //
NK041(di)037:1757: mthong zhing rig nas dben pa'i gnas su song //
NK041(di)037:1758: gangs ri'i mgul dang mthon po'i nags khrod sogs //
NK041(di)037:1759: thar 'dod skye bo'i bsti gnas nyams dga' bar //
NK041(di)037:1760: 'dod chung chog shes bsod snyoms 'tsho ba dang //
NK041(di)037:1761: phyag dar khrod kyi dman pa'i gos gyon la //
NK041(di)037:1762: legs gsungs 'dul ba'i bslab las mi 'da' zhing //
NK041(di)037:1763: rgyal sras spyod pa'i lam nas ring nas slobs //
NK041(di)037:1764: sngar bshad srol gyi lta sgom spyod pa yis //
NK041(di)037:1765: da lan tshe la btsan sa zin par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:1766: rang don nyams len rtogs pa khor yug dang //
NK041(di)037:1767: gzhan don 'brel tshad don ldan mngon gyur nas //
NK041(di)037:1768: rang gi nyams myong gzhan rgyud gdams pa rnams //
NK041(di)037:1769: snod ldan 'gro la tshul bzhin 'doms par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:1770: bya btang khas len tshe 'di'i zhen pas bcings //
NK041(di)037:1771: 'khrul zhig khas len gzung 'dzin d+r+wa bar chud //
NK041(di)037:1772: grub thob khas len rtogs pas rgyud dben pa'i //
NK041(di)037:1773: spong ba pa de 'jig rten sgyu ma mkhan //
NK041(di)037:1774: rnam dag 'dul ba'i khrims kyis legs bsdams nas //
NK041(di)037:1775: rgyal sras spyod pa'i bsam sbyor rmad du byung //
NK041(di)037:1776: gsang chen lam gyi rnal 'byor mi dman pa'i //
NK041(di)037:1777: spong ba pa de lha mi'i mchod gnas yin //
NK041(di)037:1778: mdor na grub thob rnams kyi lta sgom la //
NK041(di)037:1779: nyams len mdzod dang phyogs kyi sgom chen kun //
NK041(di)037:1780: lus kyi thal sbyar ngag gi bstod pa dang //
NK041(di)037:1781: yid kyi rjes su yi rangs lan brgyar bsgom //
NK041(di)037:1782: gzhung brgya bltas dang khrid brgya bsam pa dang //
NK041(di)037:1783: srol brgya rnams kyi don brgya 'di yin no //
NK041(di)037:1784: 'di yin 'di las gzhan du rgol na yang //
NK041(di)037:1785: rgyal dang rgyal ba'i sras kyis dpang mdzod cig /
NK041(di)037:1786: bka' drin mnyam med dpal ldan chos rat+na lak+sh+mikyi rje //
NK041(di)037:1787: khyod gzhung 'chad pas bka' drin bsab ma nus //
NK041(di)037:1788: 'on kyang 'du 'dzi'i dben pa'i nags khrod na //
NK041(di)037:1789: gang gsungs gdams par sgom pas bka' drin 'jal //
NK041(di)037:1790: 'ga' zhig log pa'i lam la dag par bsgom //
NK041(di)037:1791: kha cig yang dag lam la 'khrul bar blta //
NK041(di)037:1792: de phyir de dag rnams la snyan bskul du //
NK041(di)037:1793: cung zad zhus mdo thugs kyis dgyes par mdzod //
NK041(di)037:1794: 'di bris dge bas bdag kyang skye ba 'dir //
NK041(di)037:1795: gangs dang ri sul nags kyi khrod rnams su //
NK041(di)037:1796: ma nor lam bsgom spong ba lhur len rnams //
NK041(di)037:1797: rtse gcig bsgom pas bsgrub rgyud 'dzin par shog /
NK041(di)037:1798: gang 'di grub chen rnams kyi khrid gzhung rnams //
NK041(di)037:1799: mang du thos pa nags kyi spong ba pradz+ny+aa rasmi pas //
NK041(di)037:1800: rat+na k+au ta'i sa 'dzin pho brang nas //
NK041(di)037:1801: bsam gtan bsgom pa'i sgom chen kun la bsrings //
NK041(di)037:1802: sarba d+aa ka l+y+aa nam b+ha ba tu /
NK041(di)037:1803: thos bsam dang sgom pa 'chi med kyi bdud rtsis
NK041(di)037:1804: bzung ba'i gtam gyi ut+pala dpyod ldan yongs kyi rna
NK041(di)037:1805: ba'i rgyan du 'os pa 'di nyid kyi thog mar
NK041(di)037:1806: bstan bcos so so'i lus rnam par bzhag pa dang
NK041(di)037:1808: gleng gzhi'i skabs kyi mchan chung rags pa sogs /
NK041(di)037:1809: mang du thos pa'i dpyid gtsug lag smra ba'i nyi
NK041(di)037:1810: ma'i blo gros kyi snang bas cung zad gsal bar
NK041(di)037:1811: byas pa ste / rgyas par logs su 'chad par spro ba nyid do //
